air accessible entrance","enabled":false}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Repair services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Frank Conley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWEddpsYPhCAux58xkaVPBT9IwkCos65ERU5mbepQncDE9-ZPr4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am very happy with the work  greenhouse, plumbing and heating Did for me. They installed a new kitchen faucet. The plumber Andre was very efficient. He was in and out before I knew what happened. He cleaned up after himself and the pricing was very reasonable. Frank Conley😀","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2UIPjVWLuXPRpPXMwzG68bedUOPTHXLrJByQXgaWKW1C3Cq2W6EF1eXC_IPZ_PWgCBvI-kSQ5WvA_m6kMrwFWWsvRFEkLxGlTbgTer0hg-I2nSgITEIyru33na752BCfJP41T9i2mliWki=k-no"],"When":"2025-6-11"},{"Name":"Michael Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVpTtwUhxHmryvRsTRO92mDAjKyVRgyj97c4NlgIssS1mvpr3aJOQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Green House Plumbing was incredible. I was moving from a tank to a tankless water heater. I had a wonderful man come out and walk through to see what an install would take - everyone else tried to do the bid from a photo. He came on a Thursday, and booked my install for that Monday. The bid was competitive and, best of all, he had an idea of moving the tankless to a different location - which is exactly what I wanted, but I wasn't even going to mention it because I thought it would be cost prohibitive or impossible. 2-3 people were working on the install for an entire day, but they had wrapped up, vacuumed, and cleaned it all up by 5pm. When it was done, they gave me a walkthrough of what had been done and how the new system works, as well as gave me reasonable service timelines I should do for the health of the system moving forward.\nI'm thrilled with the new system and was thoroughly impressed with their service. I strongly recommend them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Carol Stamper","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIFN9wn8TnXT3RsVzZzYRLOakiUvynT5OW52szQ4RI0EdE8VQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve used Green House Plumbing a few times now. The first time they were the third plumber I called and the final one because they were the only plumber who identified and fixed the problem. Now I don’t use anyone else. Stay with the best. I’ve also referred them to friends who have had the same experience. Competent. Reliable.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jillian Willingham","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUP9Kdl2N78bfNtzj2j4f-glSCZ51YCTjPsBhSzxGA_mt5unTkY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great service! Fast and on time. Plumber was quick, cleaned up afterwards and best of all, solved my issue! Second time I’ve used them and would highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Connie Martin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIzhaCugenlyAi44MxcSkLB0B7D6ogm4r-fU2cu9_XTHJj4dQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After a Costco gas stove delivery went bad—although Costco did reimburse me—Costco delivery was out 3x and still couldn’t hook up the range. I called Green House plumbing and Heating.  From the receptionist to the plumbers, I couldn’t be happier with the service!  They were on-time and hooked up my stove with no problems!  I will be calling them for any future work I need.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jeansok Kim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVdS6DGnh390ILPDvJ2V6CbFn9QduQ-9WOVEKIyyDytBOURFWgA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My water tank started leaking, and Green House Plumbing and Heating was fantastic from start to finish. Their text support quickly walked me t