:[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Repair services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Vinko Wu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVu_hkfpVepo1k9Zkeqnc9Y1A64Y3h2Zr_hrljmmSdjki4ndtGk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I chose this company because it appeared when I searched “Rheem water heater repair,” which made me believe they were reliable or affiliated. Unfortunately, the service was terrible.\n\nTechnician Richard Egge charged $380.71, but the same problem returned shortly after. The company refused a free re-inspection and demanded more money instead. I had no choice but to replace my water heater entirely.\n\nThis experience felt misleading and unprofessional. I would not recommend this company.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0nYSVgT5BZLJ_sbXXn3vwbOtSmh1F5-G8ZOk0mn2sJaMj3tbQ3QYBWZsZdiIwRmaakbI-B0ZSKQZeNq9KbYX7M-fIoHBsBCrcMD1ObdYCmAQ0ri6wm6xGs6H0qKDOfvilhFZ44EJ5PETU=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0hGcwZlz4js0QktYACFpI73dW76iaRpYPvr6KyYuN_6qqBfe4U76cS6Hf74xZnHkt0bcudJ1xIxDNDRa0DGJJpWYaYA02nCGhO3W6jVYOb5QtmQEAW_fubPs79XKvamFW61PlzP5IW-yc5=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1Ug3ZOM_1DRwlbQyhLLebEGaPWYRl5gC_Tj_adDwkFlLeHRLQMbPxkpSe3MNuqRQzWqVkI9yiHJT2-Ai0Nks5B7ggC22xVwtuQgH0P7z8IQI70Ax5yzLoaEuhZ2ltE3m66CvdAfQutPKs=k-no"],"When":"2026-1-24"},{"Name":"Hugh Gerrard","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIIBag6yfIDRTB4ZTT8fNokoVyf0DjRPoZSjl54sXePjQeRXw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve used Fast for 20 years. We bought 2 Hot Water Hesters when we lived in Seattle. Now we live on Whidbey and our almost new Water Hester failed for the 3rd time. Rheem agreed to replace the unit and I selected Fast to do the install and replacement. Fast was out at the house via a ferry ride to Whidbey the next morning. We met Rodney from Fast and he started his work. He pointed out some issues that needed to be repaired and did the job. Rodney was courteous, professional, and humorous too! I will never call anyone besides Fast in regard to a Hot Water Heater and you shouldn’t either.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Susanna Cole","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNTo9FHa4EfRR_pkYRlXIIXUXVuGHrBGyT5JJA_YjWtYlqwWNn_A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The service tech Brett from FastTrack Bothell, who installed out water heater, was great. We used Fasttrack because they install water heaters for Home Depot and the quote we got from a licensed plumber was twice as much as FastTrack. After two rounds of trying to schedule service via the 1-800 fast track number on Home Depot’s website we finally scored on the 3rd try -(almost 2 months after our initial call). so that was a huge hassle. Once we did get service is was quick, professional, and efficient.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jean Gron","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKSzhho5DmEttePbNFqx5dW9m-ShtBHVqv2fzCOdh_8MfP2lg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had several conversations with Fast Water Heating; they navigated me through several of my options. I ended up choosing to replace my unit. The tech came and was able to assess the area. We chose a unit that fit and was installed the next day. They provided a timeframe for which they would arrive and called when they were on their way. The install went great, and the technician was efficient and knowledgeable. He worked quickly and maintained a clean working environment to ensure my rugs, etc., were not impacted. All in all, for having to have my water heater replaced, it was a good experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tae Jun","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIJs6ql8D5xmLxHFZujMnw0DgojWKA4ndORG9mi77qjlwpU5w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an excellent experience with this company for my water heater replacement. They were very responsive and provided clear, friendly explanations throughout the process. The best part was the pricing—the final cost was exactly as quoted with no hidden fees or surprises. I am very satisfied with the service and highly recommend them as a trustworthy and reliable business!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Erik Carlson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIAJ7Sl9jxWmy3lNKFPhhpqHwjjy8brOktjYhYJS1Q0B5xrBQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Caleb showed up incredibly fast. He assessed the situation and let me know what needed to be done to get everything done right. These guys treated our BnB property with respect and got the job done quickly and correctly. Caleb even gave me a chance to replace the drywall behind the water heater that was wet from my old water heater.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0O_uiBUzLHgZFQOtBBLqcLjiaTG4eXo14TmKbbUQdrdksEbZjySkG6_UnWVUTh2Dk3YqEBsr6q4B-i22c95jCjGvMwFSzHyCiMszjQyhKB9XJ5HF3o8FM_GVTs-TYQ6Xr9cPeYDSVCPsvc=k-no"],"When":"2025-12-11"},{"Name":"Todd Schulte","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIGjnuXKhcNxpHwbakYEyanksWmpe-iFUdNMjfvyXK4WVBopw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was able to get Fast Water Heater out on a Saturday, one day after my existing water heater went out after 18 years of service. They had my water heater size/preference in stock and Chris installed it smoothly and professionally. The end to end experience was top notch, I highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Proud One","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV_BXAfeX_dWutxbjF8bF4De-YdyGGBJN9or3HxQtfu1w_QnO8y=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fast Water Heater, is a very professional company. Starting with the phone receptionist to the actual plumber that showed up to do the job. Austin did a great job, friendly, very knowledgeable, and a he had great since of humor. They are contracted through Home Depot to do installations...Fast.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1YIFSKIndZ4SVDiB6Vwj2FWCQnQuO0CASrP6vqk7Hn86ZiXFP0Yc7bjTPMHZbcDlqRMV6YFT_MEDq6SxMOjz5q_X0I0cDNFN4zFsiH3dkP-LK73wP4ZXKxVbjH-Rx9gGJsxXnPGiPK3n8U=k-no"],"When":"2026-1-9"}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
