URkRlml5OaAxy_x9Zlihoi4CWP6Ss-oVA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fast, friendly, clean service to resolve a kitchen sink drain clog. Showed up same day and within a couple of hours of me making the call. Appreciate the willingness to offer service later in the evening, after 7 pm, and without an additional fee for emergency response. When I called around, other plumbers were done for the day and I was pleasantly surprised when I called these guys, they said they could arrive in a couple of hours. Super appreciate that they laid down a tarp to protect my kitchen and leave no mess behind.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Noa Rabin Cohen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLtKTaRPLiurVAecZnlqh07XKQWDcvvfNLtP-EeYo4xDtL2qQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Paul has been great every time I’ve used his services. I’ve worked with him multiple times and couldn’t be happier. He always shows up on time, is very communicative, does excellent work, and leaves everything spotless. His prices are also very reasonable.\n\nI recently reached out for a quote to replace my water heater, and not only did he have the best price, but when he came out, he honestly explained that it wasn’t time to replace it yet. He took the time to explain what to watch for and when it would make sense to replace it. I really appreciate his honesty and would definitely recommend him!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Xiaofei Wang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLN8I21HKuaPACKkSJgB-gRqYjl3dTSupU5x9Rzv3qRfVWhc7Lm=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I cannot recommend Pedram highly enough. We had a major main line blockage that turned out to be a nightmare scenario: a concrete slab had sunk and crushed into the pipe outside our house. Pedram came out late at night to hydro jetted the line to make it partial going so we wouldn’t have to vacate our home, which was a huge relief for my family.\nHe then returned promptly to handle the big job—digging out the broken section and replacing the pipe to fix the issue permanently. He was professional, fast, and incredibly reliable and his price is very reasonable. If you need a plumber who actually shows up and knows his stuff, ask for Pedram!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0_J6SdibyI3kRXsMCgPQPFagluMEbGoAqeetknIfSbqVeQyhD5FG4dlQmjeNIFZ1gIekWGxhYYzI8hPNXHf5tH0cttSqLIK_D37QMNZSkLz5KWoz3hvZCGH9I7O2HGJJLLRLXdQM-NjNY3=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-15"},{"Name":"Rachel Han","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIO9u4uINz9C8OgjmYkH0hDNzMJG5TuS_NiuQ1fb-nFDwoXqw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Peyman from Empire Drain Co. replaced two bathroom sink faucets for me last Friday. Peyman is nice and professional. I like how he arrived on time, provided me with an estimated time to finished the work without asking, and how we confirmed the total cost before he started working. Moreover, other things like putting shoe wraps on before entering my home and vacuuming the worksite after the work done also left me a good impression on him and his company. I highly recommend this company and Peyman.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0gu7ZIMxioQu7Hj0qg52gf0S-oi2DXMrYeN3Rr7uHgFV0KheEf9vauuSjoBDVimeF6szR1CCvWzSC5BMWJ8qCixcN3AKkP6HVxHYhuxK5tHZqBXnR5wrKJzz39LkKtqSvZ_Iv7=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn12mIxJRP7Q9Z_t1MYKdB8YhGO3BeTSt0TvPE4wp4QrncPe1nafgoBNKzK2NNYs9jGrM8dgRBa7MIYpFWbS3itMCW2DKZsqp7gRjfANFPdoWEhpnE4EIAdUcxyr-5nOcDOGzJqW4w=k-no"],"When":"2025-4-15"},{"Name":"Deborah Straka","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKm7SQaoidKZF-DgNIJAAUPAdzWE9icjPjUnd4DP0ZrXGcq9Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fantastic business! I chose them based on all the 5-star reviews, and have only positive things to say about their work at my home. They installed a new toilet, connected plumbing for a newbathroom vanity, and installed new shower trim. And made an emergency trip to fix old leaky plumbing in the wall. Prompt, reliable, knowledgeable, pleasant, patient. And fair pricing. I've found my go-to plumber!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"L Z","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXRy9qMr8PKwIFh4FgPoxfnmY8z65pAffWn83hHKz_iFAq2sUzfsw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am so thankful to have found Empire Drain Co. Last week I discovered there was a water leak in the pipes underneath the cement in the driveway, and felt very stressed out as I had no idea where to begin and how much it would cost to repair. I called a few companies on Google, and some wanted to charge a fee for coming out. I was able to get 5 companies who were willing to come and give a free estimate, and Empire Drain Co came in at the most reasonable price (a couple of other companies quoted almost twice the amount). Paul, the owner, was very clear in telling me what needed to happen, and it made me feel a lot more calm about the process. They were able to come the very next morning to fix the leak, and completed the fix in the same day.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yiming Sun","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHFO7eZqOmuUqaTbiBo6v-IZsB-hfbRTMwl0i6RKjwgJuwCz1v=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Empire Drain Co does excellent service. We had a broken sewer pipe under the foundation, and called a couple of different plumbing companies before called Empire Drain Co. The other companies had to walk away from the job because they weren't sure if they could handle the job. Paul and his team from Empire Drain Co came in and got the job done. Not only that, Paul also handled communication with Home Insurance so a big portion of the cost was covered. Throughout the repair, Paul was very responsive and transparent, and we felt he was more like a friend than just a service provider. Thank you Paul!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
