sistance","enabled":false}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Repair services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Jeanna French","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIJRvL_jrk6mJgPT-ct08j44Ss0nIRzDAEms7f0nh8qZCJnlQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I had this company come out to quote a repair for a small PVC pipe that needed to be cut out and replaced -- a very basic job with minimal material required. The plumber was here for less than five minutes to look at it, and the fix itself is simple and straightforward.\n\nThe quote they gave me was $1,295 total.\nThey stated that their labor rate was $500 per hour, even though this job would not take anywhere close to a full hour to complete. And even if it did, $500/hour is far outside the normal range for plumbing labor in this area. The remaining $700+ was quoted for parts, which for PVC is extremely difficult to justify.\n\nAs a single woman dealing with an urgent repair, I left feeling taken advantage of and pressured by an inflated price for what should be a quick, inexpensive fix. There was no breakdown that logically explained the cost, and the quote felt wildly disproportionate to the work needed.\n\nPlease do yourself a favor: get more than one estimate before agreeing to anything. In my experience, there was no transparency, no reasonable pricing, and the quote did not reflect the actual scope of the job.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn06h5wmDCLKwlhsEfeHBxXP_x10K2rwYs1ktFakVpJe6gtWCzU5LhdGdz_hVweru7ejwm_EliZEjyLIHZHLsZ1yeFVxfbp6HbrVwjk-1U_6HKCt-S5uRp5wPp-_tbWqVLYj5KJGBVCURS8P=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2eTwINlKCsZC8MfP1tZO2upd3qLhew7GSrxiyGjRF3QDWJFbwraOygDStXy-VacAnBx6PARFvYfVzSLyQsbKGOGJE5B8lY10SnSh4ozRYh9_cYlu7_GEiMoWWg-4QKTadUAW6y4GB6uCte=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0Dbl5T3rJI1Tt1DR3wvK7rXRwYSfAgruzIf51O6Ixmc1LoFUAQ_SBYP7Klep3ONaX2pS9z9A9eUJEcfs8MXld1iqN8rcLyzPN_fZvm_VEgovb_e3ALnc_37rqvpgPHYIGIxpmMHufaZByR=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn13ovs8sy5I15d9UjD5wdQpe2ghyIZ8tiD4wHrR2w8WmT-Spv2ZGvXH02nvDQ3Xa-n8-643Kf4KhGiaDc9K5-wq9-DmSvIwWoOWPeRRnEZeDX9FVJFCojzqN-IOHs3ypOcNaYCwwUghjK5i=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn12dzEvBKiS5b_vgk4etxSf23Fg_ZczDGu2WPe9XkMN3HOsGwtAmG4p6LYtLYwNa956j7mf-b4lP44K81lGv0lsUaahlnAj57R7ipnh1OHUgDsnE3I9RKKnVN1UWW2hUSPjRPOC40hm4c3Y=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn27p60qasTLVJ2quFZpgIuaq7ZpMi12BWQjRJ7nETJClv48fe0BuLB0JokeR1XcXMWQVrhm5RMulUWirRkRpYoWo3EDiYt28CtMYYJ9TiBzKICgMuMi86REEGof-vkEMq7s6CCCeYiS-ox1=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2JSMSLpNDVzGV7v-JU2K6zyptoyb5D73wyP2x-36KLoFSzIIEJ4M1Ufk9I1wqGjb_qxLGgaPI8Xau-IAM7woaQ-PVyB8iEWEM3lCOfj7wR_IsXfYs3Lz2wRz3yyA4_QvSAG8RhQobZWoks=k-no"],"When":"2025-12-2"},{"Name":"Claton Hendricks","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLZC-7K-Fo_mdiD610013A8MvZpI3UDiUMMlxG2dm1ELyS3jw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fantastic experience! They showed up the same day and got to work within a couple of hours. Tyler and Austin put in a lot of effort to clear the drain, and it was finally fixed after a few hours. Really happy with the service—highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michael Jones","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKaIz1kDv9sW8GZr5_Q7jrFBcmlq2rKJTlLInpxR4lxAsovRA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was very pleased with the service I received from Austin with 1-Tom – Plumber related to an inspection of my shower drain components for an insurance claim. Austin arrived within several hours of my call.  Austin was extremely thorough in his inspection and provided me with a great deal of useful information I would highly recommend their service.","Images":nul