 spacers. I think that’s what she called them.  She was very knowledgeable and had it fixed in no time.\n\nSummar thank you for not only your 5 ⭐️ work but also for your smile and very friendly and humorous way!\n\nIf I have any more problems, you can bet I’ll be calling 1-TOM-PLUMBER again!\n\nI highly recommend 1-TOM-PLUMBER  Woodinville, Washington.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2vb9fgjchFP8y5I-kPV9d63l_dtXWd2HU8fRUkpkFomjaJ1F7dEfNvk1s73Ql-KRycNGSBa3PBqjkkvNm3hzJ5PyQ_f_OsYdETvvmgPyP4jG7ka5SKCgF-HXXJUQdnMePvC9J7N1vaRLJZ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2cE2-HA4W9R8ZTMWSTVsSSOENjmUm7h-QuEJkPjPo3zzMrNvxgG9_BDsXhwyX2X7dVP0BOMQoP8-jNysTdYPxG0uKaAUsgccUx8sLfz1g7XyUPp49NB-Ml3u5q02B9kD-_8wR6io_p4cxS=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0lKwKCILPXfA9rCCDUvOL4TLBumvlEUDof-yS9d9rTfhSqAmxnlMJaoVqASd60VDjMh0DZh16hFMzgtWVrO0bpLdCQB5s4GsPCbEMNLwW3dL0snbEp9EQxftyzDLYTICZKQsMzx5ied2_l=k-no"],"When":"2025-7-26"},{"Name":"Stevie Birklid","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXvHAoacbDuysLt1Gtdv2RHRzD3NaBNwLDCzYsznvVvwCXXHxxgdA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Summar was great, super helpful and knowledgeable, and answered all my questions. The install went smoothly, looks great, and the new tank even saved me some closet space, without losing any capacity.\n\nI also spoke with Heather in the office for scheduling and estimate clarifications, and it was truly one of the best customer service experiences I've had. Heather didn't have all the answers for me right away, but clearly explained her process for how she was going about trying to get them and worked with me to solve any problems I had.\n\nThe price wasn't the lowest I found, but the level of service from Heather and Summar was so good I decided to go with them anyway.\n\nI hope everyone has more interactions with service providers like the ones I had with Summar and Heather.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.c