0","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great experience with Jacob from Home Service Plumbers. He cleared my kitchen drain very quickly and was extremely professional throughout the whole visit. He explained everything clearly, showed strong knowledge of the issue, and made sure the job was done right. I really appreciate his efficiency and expertise. Highly recommended!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0iCTry3fHykHs9FKqxeN8T1lJ--gFvOXXhqjaopM6pjQR0bulejQXFf0WG_wOrjlEBaqBpe7mMS6b8d0scSX7gCX9qhn_80SkUUowiRVigEU7tith025WEbqa6uixUvKA7QDYiIFu9uLo=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1RbXvLJKFka_6R9KMNPgoRe5suK6RXXOs8ysjiBWCpDHrmv7xMQU85LlvMh3A1ZObwIGKnyy1vx9sSo7SWMe4u6WoQ8xl61UZ2XdT84ymiyvVN8jPxb0mBbfSVU2kWuyH3KPG0qk-7-cbr=k-no"],"When":"2025-11-25"},{"Name":"Robert Brais","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUsap2-npcVjyW-B_I4G77_1Xy6adtyL7hNyvXkqF4S8iJWEkhe=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We recently had a bathtub installed and noticed the hot water pressure was getting weaker over time. We called for service and they sent James the same day! He was professional, friendly, and took the time to explain everything as he diagnosed the issue. Thankfully, he figured out the problem quickly and saved us from having to open up the wall and replace the valve — a huge relief. The $99 trip charge was well worth it for the honest and efficient service. Highly recommend this company for their prompt response, clear communication, and expertise!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0LEv1KgizpKywGRiBOa64Othzd21ih8KBNoIFY8Q-v6sbuwqkME0NpJkOl8a2ynLmlrpiUFx1ei40q3IjwP2MGnRSdaeTW2n1_s-uGBvn6WxkhcR2D0Aur6ADK50opzJXA84_TwIPiE8ch=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-11"},{"Name":"Chris Henshaw","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJtx8KCp9PuG3t9ys5NPTtpIxVvDP82mkugT5F-YH6vb9QyYA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My friend recommended Homeservice Plumbers because she had a good experience. My garbage disposal quit working and the drain was backing up. I called and made an appointment, and was able to get one quickly. The office called about 20 minutes before the plumbers were going to arrive, within the window they had given me and they arrived exactly 20 minutes later.\n\nOnce here, I explained the problem. Apparently the blades on the garbage disposal had quit and that was causing the backup. They fixed it and were done within 10 minutes. Because it was so fast and so easy for them, they didn't charge.\n\nThey are now at the top of my list to call. Jacob was professional, quick and gave a great explanation. But I'm sure anyone that would come from this company would be wonderful. I couldn't be happier. I will recommend them to all my friends.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Samantha Jandrisch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUZBF8zh5r1TCNQDP0zD8q6wzt0oN_5l6Rs3aQpEFJprdmbnOk3=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"So glad I decided to go with Homeservice Plumbers - I looked at a few others and decided they had the best overall reviews. We had a leaky/dripping shower for about a year and Xavier was able to fix it right away! He was super helpful, went out and got the part we needed for it, and made sure everything was working perfectly before leaving! Will definitely be calling them for anything in the future. Super clean and positive experience!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Luke Fiji","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUe6BGLQ3nonhdFtbRmox7sfkVmC3071eJJa0tkHNe5QLaST7jo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"TL;DR: They were able to get our broken water heater replaced the same day, while remaining competitive with other quotes we received\n\nWe were greeted by Winston, who came across as extremely knowledgeable and took the time to assess our issue and provide a transparent estimate. He explained that the work could be completed that same day and even offered to compete with other estimates we had already received. When the rest of the team arrived, everyone we interacted with was friendly, courteous, and most importantly, respectful of our space and our pup.\n\nThey finished the job efficiently in just a few hours and left the area spotless. It was a pleasure working with them, and I would not hesitate to reach out to them again for any future plumbing needs.\n\nThank you, team!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ramon Arevalo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLhTWkqNnOv0Jp0WKXE9jo5DWX9GwyFahcHtTeN9hFXYB5Spw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jacob was great today. He came by to inspect our kitchen drain and assess whether hydro jetting was needed to clear the pipes. He was very thorough and took the time to explain everything along the way. In the end, he determined that hydro jetting wasn’t necessary and was able to resolve the issue by snaking the pipes instead, which saved us money. He also recommended that we clean our grease trap to help prevent future issues. Thanks again for coming out today—we really appreciate it.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Xiaoyue Ding","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV7L4noUKEa-pJx8jTvLHXcOgQuni86MZ5ws2NOfPXBxas4KHee=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ethan came out to do an estimate and fixed my leaking bathtub pipe right away. The initial guess and estimate was for a broken gasket, but we only found out the pipe was actually cracked once the job started and he pulled the pipe out. Ethan didn’t adjust the price at all. Fixed the problem rather quickly.\nGreat, fast service for a great price for the amount of work he did. I’m keeping Homeservice Plumbers’ magnet on my fridge.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3Pdrpmr150mDcuPZWLYnUwtrWyajFxe-l7hPDGE0Sbwsq0_Q32K4EPgjeAcNsIAkY7o0ydYle-j0i1LSwQ6kZDDYW9ILPj-5NdZlhW63bwr2-ADnnbrhfqZUltlEzJMg4xbaHyGL5Z8No=k-no"],"When":"2026-1-10"},{"Name":"Margitta Henkes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKROkPwTUu6PZYmnZ75xwcgTj1brRMUwNby2_8_qh1WhgHjBg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They are great.  Doing an awesome job. Will Acay was here today and was very professional and easy to talk to and did a great job.  Have used them before with Tucker and Eli.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
