cKtvgMud0_sz7pfOvw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Corneliu from SOS Plumbing has done work many times for me and i would highly recommend him and his company. Quick response and very trustworthy. Will definitely use them in the future.I will actually call them tomorrow again for a blocked drain on one of my rental properties.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Svetlana Cugunova","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocID2drb-6UQS5amrvGEp3yxDETGFNNDjqC3Xsrk1xTxFFA8HzE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a great experience with Corneliu from SOS Plumbing and Emergency Services. He was very responsive and arrived on time. The repair was completed seamlessly, and he even suggested and  fixed some additional items that weren't up to code. I'm very satisfied with the service and will definitely continue to use them in the future.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Javier Pimentel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJfXLCicEWaZqBIfwy8PtQQT1FOb9OynUNsTxt8HQuHf9QZaQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I wanted to take a moment to express my deep appreciation for the excellent service provided by SOS Plumbing and Emergency Services, particularly through the exceptional expertise of Corneliu.\n\nWorking with SOS Plumbing has truly been a pleasure, and Corneliu's professionalism and knowledge in the field of plumbing and customer service have exceeded all expectations. It is evident that he is not only a skilled plumber but also genuinely cares about the quality of his work and the satisfaction of his clients.\n\nHaving Corneliu as my go-to plumber gives me great peace of mind, knowing that any plumbing issues that may arise will be handled efficiently and effectively. His attention to detail, problem-solving skills, and friendly demeanor make every interaction a positive experience.\n\nI cannot thank Corneliu and the team at SOS Plumbing enough for their reliable service and the exceptional level of care they consistently provide. I wholeheartedly recommend their services to anyone in need of plumbing assistance.\n\nOnce again, thank you for the outstanding service.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vasi Oros","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL41O3SfNEc_RUXm9UZDB9ozzCo54gSNxqX6DtK8mh-j-bPmg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Top-Notch Service from a Plumber You Can Trust!\n\nIf you need a reliable, skilled plumber, look no further! Corneliu provided exceptional service and made sure everything was done right the first time. From the moment I called, he was professional, punctual, and easy to work with. He diagnosed the issue quickly, explained the solution in simple terms, and went above and beyond to make sure I was satisfied.\n\nHighly recommend Corneliu for anyone needing plumbing work whether it’s an emergency or just routine maintenance. A true pro with great customer service!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Karen Root","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVQZ98xFtyygZKM9djHnImsRg96oL_dM7ETI4-oWOgxxN854d82=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Referred by a general contractor, and neighbor, Corneliu worked with us on a complete bathroom renovation. The referral proved to be outstanding.\n\nI am not a contractor. As such, I had no choice but to put my full trust in Corneliu, which proved to be trust well placed.  His professionalism and skill were evident throughout the project, his commitment to our satisfaction was evident by his willingness to take time to problem solve and work through changes, and his integrity was highlighted when he declined to replace a water heater that still had good life left in it.  Out of an abundance of caution, I stayed close for most of the renovation work, but found myself telling my wife that I was comfortable leaving our home full of contractors as long as Corneliu was present.\n\nWe are comforted to know we have a trusted plumber we can rely on for quality work in the future.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
