lso happy that he helped me remove something that is error-prone in the long run.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Traci Ballou","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUOm1b4M05Rr_ryHqzko2O0mWjodYM0pWdeOgE5E4Dn-XAuL85l=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Being without a kitchen for 4 months after a pipe break, I called ProMax and Evan answered the phone and immediately got me into his schedule which was the next day.  yay! He was friendly, efficient and got the job done.  I cant recommend this business enough.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1KDdgVFB9KSb7zNQuL253Dp_0-hb6x4tVRmsXo03_QEct-vGmGi48dt4h0HhiSWG11AfpvMxm9pg2-LrJQCy-KwExDO-LrnATTMutGuOEKH3Vq_aZTIubY2UbhelsOLnklIjhp=k-no"],"When":"2020-12-16"},{"Name":"valentine s.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXtfRGdTBiQq22hAxK3DTD5_7yo3d5xACGz2t8MAK-GDfMIJdfN=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Evan was very knowledgeable, professional, and did a great job! He's done a couple jobs for us already including installing a new water heater. We'll definitely have him come back out to do any future work!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Annmarie Bourgeois","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMv4PgzOOaZ6DQqWU72OMpYF6kycRBXVK9Qn2zQ-MSZeXZwOSA0w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I want to give a huge shoutout to Evan at ProMax Water Heaters \u0026 Plumbing for responding to my emergency phone call the morning after Thanksgiving to report a busted pipe under my kitchen sink.  Evan came out as soon as he could and replaced our cheap plastic pipe with higher quality material.   I appreciate Evan's promptness and quality service, along with his willingness to answer unrelated plumbing questions including what to do next step with my aging water heater.   He did a great job and kept my kitchen clean in the process.  I will call on him should any other plumbing needs arise and highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chris-Ann Wheeler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocITsxOvqsCHxNAn0Vjqny6QtDEUspWgOo4HoakKE2F47XprWg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wow and wow!! I needed to get an estimate for an incorrectly installed shower faucet handle and when I called ProMax Water Heaters and Plumbing I was lucky enough to get Evan on the phone. He quickly diagnosed the problem and offered to walk me through the correct install over the phone. Incredible! I almost thought I hadn’t heard him right. But he walked me through the process with excellent instruction, and the shower handle is working properly.  I now have hot water! This kind of integrity, professionalism, and kindness is so very rare. I appreciate Evan and will use ProMax Water Heaters and Plumbing for our next project. There’s no reason to look anywhere else!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jocelyn Ewert","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW2qV2LPaNMrXbB_Xhffw3YQu2DitQc4a5KxJpDq9FDmVUxxkeTUQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Evan and his team did a fantastic job diagnosing the problem and provided excellent service. I would HIGHLY recommend their service. I called after having a bad experience with another company who told me that my water heater needed to be replaced. Turns out it was an issue with my gas meter. So glad I called ProMax!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Stuart Jennings","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWIYHtyISHWcdqCVwk_d6noq8ZlO4OCAY3H1M-wWraPjhbPP18=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Evan and Owen have done a couple of plumbing repairs around our house, and they've done great work - very reliable. They replaced a garbage disposal, and the toilets in both our bathrooms. Responsive, skilled work, high integrity - just highly recommended.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
