den","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUYmBVOWisSJDI_6-cyUxu_Pdc9LCSZX8SV8xwIswyZeyuoeCk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They fixed my problems up really quickly; was very professional while still communicating. I won’t get into details what the job was, but it would’ve cost me a lot more than the other plumbers around Seattle. Absolutely recommend, Lance was very very helpful in explaining everything in a timely manner.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cutter Werdel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9SMGlKrRVEmFzf0K2aduFTKjcjmsBsbMVg_rSA59KrRtzGBs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you need any assistance with Plumbing and Heating then A Game is the best place to help you. I cannot thank Lance enough for his help. He is one of the most genuine, kind, and honest people you will ever meet. He will tell you exactly what you need to hear, not what you want to and he makes sure he puts in the time and effort it takes to make sure your problem is completely solved. He cares so much about his customers and team, and it shows in his work. Thank you again Lance for all your help.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Darci Evidon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLFRuNJyhwVMqCC2YlESsPjb-mcnWFCu4cWfVdI-v0GWqRgiWA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really pleased with the service I received today! Had a leaking/rotted old galvanized pipe in my dirty crawl space. Lance the owner and crew showed up in a day and guided me as to my choices to fix without any pressure as to whether to fix just the broken joint or all of the pipe. Super nice and respectful guys. Quickly got into the wet unpleasant crawl space and got the plumbing work done for a reasonable price. Very impressed, would definitely recommend them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Curt Rutland","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVKbwBDb2rYczSXj85pXvLHogLZ1MmzTjGz6HajCM