s://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLMFcJflXvo_ZayKlCaWH67vupijS2amGYCq-HYBCXRMetJFQ0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lance and his apprentice did a wonderful job on a tricky install. They explained the issues to me very clearly and gave me their expert advice on the best way to proceed. The new sink looks great and functions as it should. Honest, friendly, and competent. Can’t ask for more than that.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
