ely and made me feel at ease about it all. Scheduling the replacement and making payments were easy and straightforward - also had Apple Pay. This is my first time working with a professional to fix something in the house and I was preparing myself for some tough conversations, but Michael was very pleasant to work with.\nBeautiful website to look up services offered, very accessible on the listed number via call/text, fair pricing, excellent communication, and quality workmanship.\nIt truly felt like having a friend fix a problem at your house and I would definitely reach out to this companion again for anything related to plumbing and heating.\nAttached pictures show the new water heater, expansion tank, mixing valve, and relevant fixtures. All up to code and passed inspection.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1r8JxxEpT1V_shw_Z671OOyPw7baqBmEHHbNvZB846vU88gbIiDCgeQhEcafXN4eERLJT8xSij8ZNw1ZSTN_3149bIlxwVzFpEeu1lNXLUDrhIOKdyn_XEKGP7zoVguYGIw_3OI2MkCV4=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3b4V7aoTMkuRfaPojKODilvO03QeY14jLYymEHOSn_71Zd-RJTZBE9pXI9vWke724KOThMYnT6L5CORsmd2ETXZUcKblYRBAx1HMTTNGjNdUYcGm8rd0X51k-L05pdDuZR-FiLxh0qRi7t=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0zT0D58FamXaYTgI2aLvbBZRmL0TFM31BTR0Lq96sCh6KLV4NkvSKnn_48O2WwedohoFYnOnnIVtZCUN-_2juWsuSdxkwn48NAFfjW3cS1GzBCB0ZJAE9wYeBQhl6hV8Q0uzizbxRGv-Eb=k-no"],"When":"2025-8-14"},{"Name":"Wulf Maer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUjqN6Lg3qFQ1OKVER7IlGpUi_0QBjubMIRJQx8SHjPb0yGLjjp=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I spotted mention on nextdoor.com that this company (Companion Plumbing \u0026 Heating) was a local husband \u0026 wife endeavor and decided to try them out for the removal and replacement of a toilet and the experience was excellent! After speaking with the wife, who schedules all the jobs, the husband, Mick, came out quickly and very speedily removed my 20+ year old toilet, and then assembled and swapped in my new one, and then carted away the old toilet to include all the heavy boxing and packaging for my new toilet without issue! The pricing was also very reasonable. He also arrived in a very well kitted out work van replete with tools and parts and was ready for action! I will be doing business with this company again and heartily recommend them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Stephen Willingham","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKGQzxUcRKhI0MOuMmdgufkoVxY7xUdjLSY1soXXRkALYCEQA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great experience with Companion. Highly recommended.\n\nWe had an emergency break on a water line that required water to the house to be shut off. Mick went out of his way to fit us in the  same day, repair the problem, and restore the water. Great resource to have in the Sammamish  ommunity","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marshall Dean","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUJSs-WKv6TZ1aeho6NZeeQypZnFGNNhlcKNe8a_G2QnXD1gEBPbg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the most efficient and pleasant professional experiences I’ve had in a long time. I contacted Companion Plumbing for an inquiry and promptly received a response from Mick to investigate what was going on. We decided he would come out to take a look and booked a site visit the same week.\n\nHe quickly determined what needed to be repaired and/or replaced and thoroughly walked me through my options, including their pricing. I felt confident trusting him after we talked about the why, how and if you don’ts.\n\nHis time estimate was spot on and he had repaired some complicated hydronic piping within two hours. He even took the time to diagnose another issue on top of why I originally called him out. He’s personable and absolutely knows his trade and I will recommend him to all my neighbors without hesitation.\n\nSave yourself the headache from shopping around, just go with Mick! You’ll be impressed.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0CQMOZQ-bqNsKg4nGJf7ikTgTLevj9rz2wHwhNY_5z2rBnMcptipWMZeqBkV107L-5Bz9Gy6ZkxRGyBB3jmXWJfWhcNeibHiPY3AuHaP1dVO-RPl-lkz_Uv2upzzN9-Qfy2H5s=k-no"],"When":"2025-5-23"},{"Name":"Rich Rye","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV3vUtIKxV7AWQJZHYrgtwTe27yEeasHORgXumZE5_ovNyfQzS8tA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We cant thank the team at COMPANION PLUMBING enough Mick was absolutely great to us. We had a mysterious smell in our home that woukd come and go. We had some work done in a bathroom a few months back by\nanother company and that's when the odor started shortly after. We had them back to try to figure it out and they could not, they said everything looked right but it sure didn't smell right. Mick did some investigation removed vanity and looked into how the plumbing was done on our back to back bathrooms and was able to identify there were problems with the way the vanities were plumbed and the venting source, which was ultimately causing our mysterious odor.\nCompanion Plumbing was fast to schedule with, very friendly and also fairly priced and we appreciate it!!\nWe definitely recommend them to anybody with a problem or a project they would like help with.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jen Wilhelm","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV1oy3PzJsref_zc09HgRPPCML_6fsl3_MyQ-rn3gfPNi75du_6=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Some pipes in our garage began leaking due to a failure in the pressure regulator. We called Mick in the morning and he was able to stop by the same day for a repair which was great because we were losing a good amount of water and were worried about other pipes in the home bursting due to the increased water pressure. He replaced the broken regulator and installed a more reliable main shutoff valve (which actually looks like a shutoff valve compared to the plastic junk we had before). Mick was extremely friendly, knowledgeable, and professional and had us back up and running in just a couple hours. He also helped us troubleshoot a small issue with our dishwasher, free of charge. We are very happy with Mick's work and he will be the first person we call if we ever need additional plumbing work!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1JD11orcic4Od93F1ciqSrCix-aLjbhtLsaBUirpbiR_eHvtnITdQ5RwnWPRiTNlJM9S5f2MgENRVQ0Tjai-XRvriOxvlRMEE706ZLJvRgMn5pl5ZDb25F3RPV7O_D3KLh6K7vmQ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3NCv2ysnLJRL2pvKBwJCmdM_zStcK-U--7o___iMKdriaseljh1Q1fefBqKKB2qLAApprRnrkDCtyZAjFlo5SgouNChi2ioKfYXZZQlddVHZtH1a0RrSsCOxNgPPEe3BAndQAS=k-no"],"When":"2023-10-2"},{"Name":"Peng Zhao","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU-fLAw8oG7qYbdZUrm3SZnOuttV3evnzostJxyRUD_H7n-Nhlm=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Mick helped repair our front yard leak. It required some digging and fixing. After American League detection located the spot, Mick was able to come and fix the leak in the same day within two hours. I’m really impressed with his efficiency and I really appreciate his upfront communication about different possibilities and repair options.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Linnea R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwO4OPOZ-tESzNFexx-_C_LjAktI94UxoBIaL2vWMvW0Z3rhQH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was great - Mick was very personable and professional, and I could tell he has a lot of plumbing knowledge and experience. I was confident it was getting done right. The scheduling for the consultation and actual work were both very easy. The woman on the phone when I called was also super friendly and helpful. Happy I found them and would definitely hire them again!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
