nt.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAFE7Bnhu8rv8zzdRtt38L-f1_J29inRM-1817Ok-B-9geER53S113gsFETsY1z1nSp1eiA4hgYQ5iom6F1OapmKs5sQxaAh58s4fX5dQAmhQLMN8h4j4J6UkmTfCn4kh2e5xKYc=w397-h298-k-no"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"118248027971809003624","name":"Rez The Builder - Handyman/Contractor (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/118248027971809003624"},"complete_address":{"borough":"","street":"","city":"","postal_code":"","state":"","country":""},"about":null,"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Elsie Papenfus","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKmMcWklhi943LfrdkSBVy-hnqjpggaZRkayhFTM0dD7Cte0w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Based on all the positive reviews, we reached or to Rez to fix some door casings in our basement and do some touch-up painting. He was quick to respond and arrived on time for his initial assessment. He had good availability and was flexible to accommodate our schedule.\nHis communication was clear and he completed the job within a day.\nI will reach out to Rez again if we need a handyman!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Adem Burak Yazar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJkIRzPTKPdod9gmRkenh6sHzRRCsYZVf_V6xH29mJSwOilbw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Reza is a great guy, he replaced our garbage disposal. He has knowledge about new and old type of house harnesses so he made a really clean jobs and definetely will call later for other needs. Thank you.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"R C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLdXK1UUmboUi2h16tPF5P9HVvl6o9VPQ6UCiwk-0oA_gXKPA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Extremely pleasant experience.  Rez communicated from start to finish.  We had issues with entry door mechanism, shower fixture, and bedroom closet.  Rez resolved all issues quickly.  He was extremely professional and courteous.  Hopefully, we will not have any future issues, but we will reach out to him for sure if we do.  A+ service!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mitchell Rausch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXchzks6MF-JDlXEIfzBewCcWpaPkx_jfv2TwqERBboWyrzPojS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent service! Rez was very responsive over text and provided clear updates while on-site. Rez replaced a broken fence post and got my gate back in working order. Fast, professional, and effective. I’ll definitely use Rez again!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cathy S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL8zNNDmOm6IATwIVbilcUMDQb0qHrLL68YrqMhdgRMO-7iQg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Rez is very reliable and prompt to respond to our request. He helped us installed four faucets and curtains nicely. We appreciate his great work so much!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"bhem19","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWIbZY2OR_MPzeepGtJgcMB-afijdueqXLy-XbL3fpDdd8M0iM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Rez did an excellent job framing and installing drywall, as well as painting an exposed HVAC vent in my daughter’s closet. He also replaced three bathroom exhaust fans and updated several light switches throughout my home. He was punctual, respectful of my space, and very professional. I’m extremely happy with the results and would highly recommend him to anyone in need of a skilled handyman.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aishwarya Venkatesh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUxQvqrIGg2SvQdNXNAKZll7G_o9C1mgnuTEuHI9aC4zmWBKZan=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We reached out to Reza for help installing our new microwave in the wall cabinet. Reza responded almost immediately, made time to stop by in his schedule the next day and did a fantastic job.\n\nThe unit was larger than the cabinet opening, but Reza was very nifty in figuring out a solution - he removed the outer wooden frame, guided the microwave in, reattached the cabinet and screwed in the microwave frame. Reza figured out how to put together the vent attachment in the limited space without compromising on function. We also had to do some trial and error with the drilling into the frame that left the microwave frame very slightly askew, which is my only nitpick about a job otherwise very well done.\n\nOverall we are very grateful to have it installed and the job finished in a timely manner.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kamil K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJsfyiI0dvp1zMB9due7owPvNLeU1l8-6fxiKizyaYCkO4sGQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Reza fixed a broken floor joist in my home and a leaning fence post. He did an amazing job.\nHe connected the broken joist with screws and then sistered it with two 2x6s (one on each side). All of that secured with multiple screws and sitting properly on a beam.\nFor the fence repair he removed the rotten post and dig a hole deep enough to have it at the same level as neighboring posts. After that he filled the hole with moderate about of cement. He used an extra piece of wood to secure the fence and keep it leveled. Also replaced joist hangers since the old ones were damaged.\nThe end result is perfect.\nHe's polite, professional and always on time. Easy to talk to. He even spent good 30 minutes to discuss my private project, and a few problems, and gave me a few great ideas.\nI definitely recommend Reza.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0D7PnyhVtBo7TIT0o5VXGh74lPgHxG17uyf_qLHJbIg6ywcz9F06O7fxk8zGiodiokxPjdBOrJYJXzff2qyV5_qk6zMUXReb6d6z8mDSiu0N1Y3rEI8SebrGIEJtHLGNterHM=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2Byl89otHzEB2cBSnxemFbwINHhxLs5ZBwBUhoOhSd2WuUC0l9cIU-0aa9f5dCpffbgsrULbTuJy6BCysM6uXradOtUcmIJt14vvHMUpR2xjyvKDCWEIqVHANjlUoNS0T1SXo_pg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3wtHfY8eaU6C45KddUts-tGigAS215mFEcJU0XLwyqgaoaksMewgFUtOF8YRUhGHb8o7xg9-B