NQkAEg6L9I7--8ZaSU5Hs-O743SZol3vRxFOU4z7TQKplYlsCCtTuGIicusfk2THtJ-6vYfUQDZ1qnaTQn8qBUPoSMn-U7B5pn4N6-1QPjoIoR7vBBuhio-AhGOFvzqTQHQxRTdwds=w224-h398-k-no"},{"title":"Inside","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAEo1tM9ACMB3tvYq_4mntkIk5ga3iSMFB6EjIvpXwteKlOv2HXA2xZbKN8fsUzWSUSa9XUa5E1I3awU96c7CMlo5YLrUITJGrT7Bz00hmalIVybIrjmYbcssMS1UfZX4iWpXT8=w224-h298-k-no"},{"title":"By owner","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAEYJBJI76q80Iu4JKQ0d5VBSbGovOh7mm0eXsUV4c-QGxiDSIeyzNyqdCGLb7hVRl7k61LS0KVVN4vpAyGTpmgZpJKACOWB_1iGbRoGPJuXgXVQUv2hBhHgBOlI4k3INuIOxPgofldPNJ9i=w224-h398-k-no"},{"title":"Street View \u0026 360°","image":"https://streetviewpixels-pa.googleapis.com/v1/thumbnail?panoid=O5QEv_KyAg4Dc0gvYAup3g\u0026cb_client=maps_sv.tactile.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=298.15994\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"102950900000738518657","name":"American Rooter Sewer \u0026 Drain Service LLC (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102950900000738518657"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Lake Hills","street":"1623 151st Ave SE","city":"Bellevue","postal_code":"98007","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Online estimates","enabled":true},{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":false},{"name":"Language assistance","enabled":false}]},{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Shinny Ip","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKz9kazJfCb8lv8UZrHglq0z2rrk9oUbpTWhCHMrDja61kqDA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I cannot recommend Ron highly enough! He recently handled a plumbing issue for us and displayed a level of professionalism that is hard to find these days. From the start, he was incredibly transparent and honest about the work required.\n\nWhat impressed me most was his commitment to his word; even when the scope of the project unexpectedly increased, Ron stuck to his original quote without hesitation. He took the time to do a thorough walkthrough of the issues I was facing and explained the 'why' behind the solutions he proposed. If you want someone who goes above and beyond and truly puts the customer first, ask for Ron.\n\nIf you are looking for a plumber, you can actually trust, look no further than Ron - American Rooter Sewer and Drain Service.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Richard Hughes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX5T29ic3_nCu8vCXsl5Dw-t2uE2AuJAP5augSakGxUyWELYd8o=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ron is a great guy, and super responsive. I sent him a tentative email looking for a quote on Saturday, not expecting to hear anything before Monday and within an hour he replied to give me him a call. \"I can come out tomorrow morning. Sunday morning\" . He turned up exactly as he said on time, took one look at the drainage swail and said \"I'm going to run a camera down right now whilst I'm here\". Never mind the quote. He was able to do a video for us of the pipe and show that it hadn't got damaged and this was all in less than 24 hours. Absolutely stunning service would definitely use him again. Great guy! Great company! Great communication! Great to work with.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aaron Dupre","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU2CksCEUTJVbT-U-pTkf-QoKyCbGfjEuB-qThgjA3KwTOOWjmv3Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is who to call when your line is backed up. Ron was amazing with my difficult piping situation. He was able to get it hydrojetted and rip all the roots that had grown through the pipe. Great guy, who really knows his stuff. He also had the best prices from the quotes I got.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Neil Penwell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ_FjPA-xHOBxlD1VShMyKwmQ946ycPqNqoo0hv9UoqQ32qeA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My side sewer line was completely blocked by roots.  Fortunately, Ron was able to come by that same afternoon.  He was very friendly, explained everything very clearly, and was very thorough in his work.  He went above and beyond what others have done.  He did excellent work, and I am very pleased!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nancy Reim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIQu9Pt-LvTDRSaLu7KXHeQST_HZpj-ObQ84FPRanN1q3RmZg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ron was great to work with! I hired him to hydrojet the drains at my parents’ house, which often get clogged with roots and mud. I’d used another company before, but always felt that they weren’t very honest, thorough, or punctual. Ron was the complete opposite - he was transparent, detailed and dependable.\n\nI really liked that he’s the owner and the one who came out to do both the estimate and the work (no middleman). He walked me through everything, let me watch the camera inspection, and explained what he was doing the whole way through. He cleared out a root plug and even flushed the connecting pipe to the neighbor’s house. Super thorough and professional. I highly recommend! Thanks Ron!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michelle Dupre","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVltuFADLS8NQHygR8FYPPDZDlEnaTjN6Xs3e07UH2yBsP4T63g_A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a backup that had water draining down through a light fixture in the basement. My husband called Ron at 8:30 am and Ron arrived by 10:30. Ron snaked a camera through the drain and found roots taking up residency. He hydro jetted the drain pipe and cleared the drain for a very affordable price. Highly recommend Ron with American Rooter!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ehsan Iranmanesh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXA4pBBhH7l4u7hewVgeZpyFr-baIcGUCjQltBnouoVyMDZrjwO=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ron recently came to my home for a rooter service to unclog the main driveway drainage, and I was extremely satisfied with the results.\nHis work went above and beyond expectations — the quality was exceptional, and the price was very fair, making the entire experience an excellent value.\nI’m thoroughly pleased and would highly recommend his services to anyone in need of plumbing help, especially for tough drainage issues.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Margret Graham","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLE_OuHcTNZsQgscFRht36sPHNALg6fh6-jb7VLi0ctlftgOg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Highly recommend! Ron was incredibly responsive, competent, pleasant, reliable and affordable. He was the only one who could come out to the boonies on a holiday to deal with a septic backup, and then returned the following week to install a new tank. Then we had a problem at our own place in the city, and he came promptly and cleared the drains quickly. Will call him next time and all the times.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
