rsons there would rather take calls than talk to customers, and when you finally get a response from them you are welcomed with dismissive belittling behavior.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Laura B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLxE_hEJU3cJvjD016LMijrTt-z2a_RsrvnNy-l6XHK6BP39j8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Extremely rude staff. Dismissed me right off and had no intention of making me a customer. Zero stars\n\nJokes on them because I immediately drove to Ferguson’s and within 20 minutes, completed my $2,000 purchase.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sean Daly","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWLaEtbCRETa_MpcPvqikbZTzfbpDGlCLiQNFIJ_Qgp9hDc6uAQVQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They're always helpful to plumber contractors this is not the place for DIY Chuck the managers a good guy and the front desk help is excellent along with the showroom plus you can always see Fred next door for heating and air needs","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sarah","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLc7lhMlYCzDV9SdXRumw16Pc1hRz5magU-iAnct7bfmmVDfQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Went in to the showroom for my kitchen remodel. Lady at the front desk kept taking phone calls rather give the customer in front of her so much as a minute of time. Not impressed.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kileona Manzano","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJEF5of8xFgpilB2jHNES49_5qGmqROMrdopf1frdxk0ALzoatE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dillon went above and beyond to assist me with the parts I needed. Very professional and curious.  Two thumbs up 👍🏽 👍🏽","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dan Wymer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWKOyon-g4GmNCJeJ4-No-XapxPwWnMmpe0s7i01Og3LHqau50=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Called looking for a good reverse osmosis faucet and they had no