tion, and Daniel as the project manager made the process highly organized and professional. Daniel began with a detailed consultation, inspecting plumbing, electrical layout, subfloor integrity, and moisture exposure before recommending upgrades. He provided a clear written scope covering demolition, plumbing and electrical rough-ins, waterproof membrane installation, tile work, vanity and fixture placement, and final inspections. Daniel supervised each phase carefully, ensured compliance with local building codes, and maintained consistent communication. The crew followed a structured workflow, kept the job site clean and organized, and executed each task with precision. The finished bathroom is modern, durable, and reflects both craftsmanship and thoughtful planning.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"CLARENCE MOLINA","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIKvPYRl6cb74ZSd9fbJKrqVoxGAjHstKnslIcCaRYsqnbBLw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently hired Best Home Remodeling for a full bathroom renovation, and the results exceeded my expectations! The team was professional, detail-oriented, and completed the project efficiently. They listened to my ideas, offered great suggestions, and left my bathroom looking modern and beautiful. Highly recommend their remodeling services!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"CHRISTUFF CRAUZ","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIIhUemdjtnjatQvZf_Zj5adXZLvJ6bJUKGQ_ueP2WZ5h54Lg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Our home door lock was sticking, so we booked a service. Home Services Plus arrived promptly and adjusted it perfectly. They were courteous and professional throughout.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"CHRISTIAN ANGELO DOMINGO","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJeiX1D6s19dCQnT75_4Uwdg_KHmfInEQMWnNkBX1jbODHSbf8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of our ceiling fans suddenly stopped working and started making noise. Instead of replacing it, we called for repair service. They diagnosed the issue fast and completed the fan repair the same day. Saved us money and the fan works like new again","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nancy Woodard","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL_63eYjiHhd3cFWku26ojhiPdvkGXjiclMH4prU8ymgeH9DQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a persistent leak in our master suite that was causing structural rot. David didn't just patch the leak; he guided us through a full bathroom remodeling project. He ensured the blueprints for the new drainage were perfect and installed Kohler fixtures and a custom stone walk-in shower. The craftsmanship in the marble tile work is stunning. It feels like a luxury spa.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"chrisiannelouisse yaneza","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLsKNUZRTMBwIez4bXKtRlXdpDgluuFuc7dURNZJWzkgDLNvQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best Home Remodeling did our exterior paint and trim work. It feels like a brand‑new home, and neighbors have already complimented the upgrade!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
