 to work with in every way.\n\nAbsolutely without a doubt the best plumbers we've come across.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kristen Kohashi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLlHkOa05cUENV0qLj-pLJSiSGNa-J-woi0SVZa1igCdJ2raA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My coworker recommended King Plumbing and I had a great experience working with them!\n\nThe shower handle and faucet in my condo apartment were leaking. I originally intended to replace all of the hardware while fixing them at the same time, so I contacted King Plumbing and around 10 other Seattle plumbers to ask for estimates.\n\nKing Plumbing was THE ONLY plumber who replied with a detailed and transparent estimate about how much the work and parts might cost! Every other plumber wanted to charge me $35-150 just to come out and look at my condo (of course the fee would be \"waived\" if I chose to hire them, and I'd lose the money if I didn't). After a while, I realized that my dreams of replacing all of my shower hardware would be out of my budget. I contacted King Plumbing again and they suggested just replacing the cartridge in the shower handle for much, much cheaper.\n\nJulie, the wife and office manager, was so knowledgeable and helpful when it came to recommending parts and the work that could be done. I really appreciated her quick responses via email and her transparent pricing for the different types of work I could have done.\n\nTwo guys came out to my condo this morning and quickly fixed the shower handle. When it looked like the faucet was still leaking and needed to be replaced, they ran back out to their truck and brought in a matching replacement faucet that they luckily had on hand. They installed that with no problem, and only charged me an extra $20 for the part and installation, instead of nickel-and-diming me for the extra work. The total came out to more than $200 less than the quote I got from one of their competitors.\n\nThank you, King Plumbing! I'll be recommending you if any of my neighbors need work done!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Zachary Rubin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL_lsaLK6hf5ABT68wyCrj1aOPLmI4x2w2ZjKbpWNBlU93UxQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The team at king plumbing is incredible and here is why they always get my business:\n\n1. Julie communicates incredibly either via email or phone. She always follows up!\n2. I've used the squad for 2 different projects, working with different plumbers. Both plumbers call in advance to advise when they would be arriving, arriving when they said they would arrive and crushed the projects quicker than expected\n3. when you add in fair prices to the above, it's a no brainer to use King Plumbing!\n\nEven when I have projects that don't initially need their help they ALWAYs provide guidance, recommendations and questions to ask!\n\nThey've got my return business!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Derek Bracy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWxPE3u-4ek-oQtii6EcejuSQIUfrb8E6A_v3b_r-DVOxoMg-DJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Josh and his wife Julie run a top notch business!!  I hired them a few months back to install a new dishwasher in my home which did not have one previously.  Installation was flawless and Josh was very professional and courteousness throughout.  I Recently elected to use them again for an entire Bathroom remodel, for which I am a complete novice.  Josh and Julie have walked me through every detail of the process answering flurries of my questions and providing hands on consultation along the way.  I cannot recommend King Plumbing enough, a real class act!  I will continue to use them for all my plumbing needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Laurelann Khadder","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL4NTBjw42uXJKIxahoBWEFOtNLpakYjoXOrTwC-7fpQIc8cw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"King Plumbing is amazing to work with, and I highly recommend them to anyone. They’re very committed to ensuring they address your concerns. They communicative clearly and transparently from appointment booking to outlining fix options and pricing. I’ve had to do a lot of work my home this past year and they are the only company that I don’t dread needing to call when something new comes up because I trust them and their work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jennifer Shutts","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWktebBOFdVD_6jvV7kUvWLFSXRU4Tm5tfmq3J6jql6b0WD94ba=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing experience.  Calling a plumber has never yielded a good experience until now.  They were recommended by my neighbor.  Julie on the phone was so lovely and respectful.  The guy who came to assess my problems fixed them after discussing with me.  He was nice, honest, knowledgeable.  The process was a great experience and reasonable.  I will not hesitate using them again","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
