performing at a very high level — which speaks directly to the quality of their workmanship.\n\nThrough everything we’ve been navigating, Matt and Jessie have been steady, responsive, and solutions-oriented. They didn’t just complete a job — they helped restore confidence and stability to our facility.\n\nWe’re extremely grateful for their expertise and support.\n\nThank you, Matt and Jessie.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2faKHWprnAXYi7MpnUQgcKLNdJGQSNqPrfyrY9aF274UQvJFaOa8GMDxMD8QJm4jI-N8HLTs3rUMh8e7KM82zZesAX-XA_YSxaUbsqoM3X8bpo2L2wPAQz5O1c32UylOqSvg9OV3KGhbZP=k-no"],"When":"2026-3-2"},{"Name":"overcome Smirz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWAkV5UXB2LOg2Y3JqULWf2rCDRjjOHFMGUhishZ_N5zFX5s2jQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have never had a pool company be as thorough and as meticulous as Independently Dunn, LLC\nThe owner's jessie \u0026 matt are awesome people! Matt came out to my house and literally went above and beyond to take care of my pool. Matt knows anything and everything there is to know about pool's. After he was done he stood in the rain and explained in detail to me the issues with my pool.\nMatt's wife Jessie was amazing to speak to on the phone. She was very helpful. She’s a pleasure to talk to. this work ethic is reflective of great leadership. In today's world where service is lacking in so many areas, independently Dunn LLC excels and sets the standard!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kathy S.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI-LX316hnauIeufJiVs_fOCCaoGvlVT4kNPKclhU-53iuNDg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had frozen pipe from a bad winter storm. The broken section was in a very awkward spot at ground level inside the drywall in a very crowded utility room. Mathew identified the leaking problem and fixed it nicely. He also fixed some issues that always puzzled us. In addition he taught us quite a few things about how to keep the pool running efficiently. It was a very pleasant experience working with them. One more thing, I like how they schedule the service visit. It's a two hour window but they texted me ahead of time with a precise arrival time. I have no hesitation recommending they to my friends and family.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Molly Russell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLKUSW2yLkeJzFhPmi4rSZD0sX3qEIKrtaUS9ZgTbuz6uY5Pw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I started using Independently Dunn this spring - 2024 and they have been nothing but amazing to work with. They are honest with prices and very helpful start to finish. They are hard workers and make sure they job is done well and correctly. They are safety focused and it shows in how to approach their job. I feel lucky to have found such a great service.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Overcome Smirz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX5lUYKW-TG2UUO0XGbZHjbecyph8LqLRChePxDONY9gege6ts=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"These guy's are awesome. I've used them twice already.\n\nJessie is a lifesaver! I called this company to assist with my pool as it started looking a little rough. jessie  was so professional and attentive, she cleaned the pool and filter's, balanced my pool and it looked brand spanking new again! They are fast,friendly and reliable. If you want a great pool company and a amazing experience call matt and jessie.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Edmond Yue","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLxUUdYXhbL65FAwe7Hz-DDru1HCSXt0paIssZqwyhtZW3-WQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We were complete pool newbies when we brought our house. Our pool was in pretty bad shape and Matt and Jessie were a tremendous help in getting it back to swimmable shape and helped us understand the ins-and-outs of pool maintenance.  With their help we established a long term plan to modernize our pool and they wer