 instructions. He suggested Speed Queen with dial controls. Great appliances and surprisingly quiet. I think they will last us a long time. After almost 6 months of regular use we could not be happier. Great low key customer service with  no pressure to upsell. They also have a repair service onsite. Would highly recommend them - a family owned business.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1ZQQ0fQNW6m9eh_f0JATG5Y30QBuqtDYUKsIVYNmVeKpasr2m1KIjV7le-0TAl0fhUlUkddG5yp2SMwUGfDnFmEx6XpgMUfEhFBAV-z9ltON2QP9DlXi7fNTWcY4pZr4HyyMvoabcCEY8=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn23mLVxiW7xaOyQMwW0E6Z_5eovtMEjGKXcnFPpUVOjES8Q22Ow7QElPqWCDZJJzAl0mP8cAM8WTU7ryFW3Hhu7aQsdZvcB43jGuHVuRoFRC6eXJFBbaZRWme4gVmppAQ7jLKeUl2P0yA5R=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2YBzZ1rhsJavBdot5vVJ4WI4qsyT82tS_k9zHs85Mv9tQB1Uwzz1lOi5J8mu0Z0xCItf8FdQZeVoBN2-KTrm0nhNmCzCFWt12Dk-Ebm2rPLIVqH5VGiimQqTtl5157kffJeHVFXG9yEtqH=k-no"],"When":"2025-8-9"},{"Name":"John Phillips","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU6VcwsFV7rifHJYG8zrafC4O32Ple_bvr58cc5y2L-1ZTNsKHk3w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Chris and Brian did a great job installing my washer, dryer and closet steamer. They were very personable, hard working and thorough.\n\nThey both advised me on the best way to set up these three machines next to each other. I appreciated their consultation because they had the best idea for the machine configuration.\n\nThanks again Chris and Brian. You guys are great!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kerry M. Hodnett","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVcPqfj5dobSVJ0dUEyFT-IaDZwvKDnhP4x08CZI8ZsCS2uE1Zd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Frederick's Appliance Center in Redmond provides excellent service!\n\nMy wife and I are repeat customers of Frederick's, having purchased LG stacked washer and dryer, on 2026-02-14, to replace LG stacked washer and dryer from Frederick's that we bought in 2005.\n\nRichard Steele was extremely helpful during the sales process; and Ryan, Bryan, and Abraham provided excpetional installation service, and all four (Richard, Ryan, Bryan, and Abraham) were gracious, courteous, very knowledgeable, and a sheer delight to work with!\n\nI highly recommend Frederick's Appliance Center in Redmond.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Craig Brown","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUdgwpSVzKGDhVgDZiAJvseNxQb7e5wjLaMfX6k-cAPO7YuAjNkgA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited Frederick’s Appliances in Redmond, WA, and had an another outstanding experience. Unlike major retailers like Costco, Home Depot, and Lowe’s, Frederick’s had the Bosch dishwasher I wanted in stock, avoiding the 5 - 21 day delay elsewhere. Jackson, one of their knowledgeable staff members, expertly guided me through the features of various Bosch models, helping me find the perfect fit for my needs. I opted for a convenient pickup the same day, as I planned to install it myself so I bypassed delivery and install. And since Waste Management allows a once a year bulk item pickup where I’m at in Kirkland, I’m getting it hauled away for free. The entire team was friendly and helpful, making my shopping experience exceptional. I highly recommend Frederick’s Appliances for anyone seeking reliable service and immediate availability on a ton of models. This is the second time they’ve exceeded my expectations and I’ll definitely return for my future appliance needs!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mariana R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKwz8DIeaIxfNhP4kkbu5U2o8bsenHEPwgQwhNyihbYKfV4_g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We worked with Frederick's Appliances to replace a dishwasher in our home. The first one we received was damaged, which only became apparent after installation. While we were quite frustrated, Frederick's took the steps to make it right and replaced the dishwasher, including reinstalling for us without an extra charge.\n\nWe are thankful and have been really enjoying our nice dishwasher. We will consider Frederick's a local go to for future appliance needs","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Quynh Le","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIR1aQzLYW9GHuYBmUr3LIV1hYxqAsvpkYLrMIZOQCg-ulRKw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"From start to finish this was the best experience I have had with my appliances.\nThe rep on the phone was professional and knew exactly what Cove dishwasher I needed and he even ensure that we had an outlet for the dishwasher. When we didn’t have one, he ensured that his technician was qualified to install a new outlet. Other places couldn’t have done this. The person who came to install our dishwasher was on time and very professional. He put down rugs to protect our floors. He did a great job. When there was a board that stuck out, he thought outside the box and cut it so it would look cosmetically appealing. Really happy with the service from A to Z. Would recommend them!!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0qu7dderDuwSp1YUEbHt3qCunYWaDNBxQzNMjm2hJvvaUgh3wrNqER4KBsIKbF64amCwevZHt1wp2Woj_2HuSV0XMuyK_ScjByLThJxgOAvanp79MKmjxOloqmadTVyznBV3mo-A=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1zCT8iw3d6tloUmQSPFaXJ3z15lfkaoZtqcH27mPhgDLiS6miA7kdraz-pf9wsscFw87r4YwBbZo0XKqeWH1ceUsCjwG0ucW1TjrfEY-xeqzzcjlZ1x8jv6-HNbJMsSUHD4cIL=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0OAIfgB8LyIzmDyjxFzPXzTQrFm1JF6U39IUXjsO8MechasBgexOITALFU6cvgVNR7bdJdIsHK7nIm_Y_TcORR1rK8uCwcoHdynVpq5je6y7RhzdhexL6-ur5VifBCqE6lCi-lmQ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0eSh4BUXTZi8MwTbCEKBlZInNaRl-85hSMSMl78z4caB_XDQ0RkgMDBNWoQgR21yCWwxsp3Ug1Y4P08myY4GMIkadfj16Tf2ovYIRd2Fhf0D-K0WGpmsevl8lE1GYsju76Fcz6=k-no"],"When":"2024-10-18"}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
