","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Dan Bond","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIXuQM-AOs2q6D8qEeYHHlo2px-dr5ZuS6H2w21rgDVE1WDmA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jonathan and his team were simply outstanding from my initial drop off and conversation of options for tuning up our 25+ YO vacuum thru Jonathan's drop off of the our like-new vacuum to our home!  The options shared were honest and reasonably priced.  The tune up was completed in 2 days.  True customer service and job well done by the entire team.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joseph McCullough","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLUL-gNBGcxApPQ1S-zYQ_929vGVWnLaMPpI7z8si2GrLU6GQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We went there not really knowing what we were looking for, but Steven was great and answered all of our questions. He even found a carpet sample just like ours at home to test the vacuums. He showed us all the features and maintenance involved with our new vacuum(very helpful, since our old vacuum broke due to our not knowing things like that). Fantastic experience all around, and we fully intend to return for repairs or replacements in the future.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chuck/Annie Driesbock/ Brown","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX1FA1q29mbbr2hwzqlbk_U0ekt4LnLEYby6uH1OY7U-1PVbGk6Mw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It's very unusual to find a store with this level of service. They truly care about their customers and go out of the way to help them. I brought a carpet cleaning machine to them to see if it could be fixed they source the part repaired  the carpet cleaner. For a minimal charge and had it ready in under 24 hours. I've been in this place three or four times and each time they have exceeded my expectations plus they are just nice people!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Viviane Pinto","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJqVqhhFmoO0voiMoVY3AvSjALC78gMmOGan8LWa-TZwiUXSA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The service was 100%. They fixed part of my vacuum in 10 minutes.The customer service was excellent, and the overall service was great. We have worked with them before and had a very good experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"P M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJBJMX0Wb6gZikbKz56BOzJuPV8kDReqpuOcwsE6KK6Ur6O7Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Inquired about a failed central vacuum on a Thursday and had a new system up and running the following day.  Jonathan provided excellent service all around.  He initially troubleshot the existing system, confirming exactly what the issue was.  While fixable, I decided the 25 y.o. vacuum was due for an upgrade.  Throughout the process Jonathans' #1 concern was ensuring we were happy with the service, the process and the end results.  We have utilized Redmond Vacuum several times over the past 30 years and continue to appreciate their focus on superb customer service and overall excellence.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shu Cravy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXxpddlzu9bPOQEYY6_ZAOJqKHwBCSFAXfXwXiqAP7QOdKWWG2Sfw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Johnathan is super friendly and helpful. Got me exactly what I was needing and for a great price! The store itself is conveniently located, and the retro aesthetics are immaculate.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lydia Choi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJIV2cp7c0tB-677oaxKs7zAYzyTTX4UZ9L_6fQTYoYrJdtCA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came in here today because my cordless vacuum wasn’t functioning properly. Jonathan and the other worker (forgot to ask for his name!) were so knowledgeable and helped me understand what kind of vacuum works best for the type of carpet I have. They helped me find the perfect one within my budget, and I’m actually excited to vacuum now. I’ll definitely be back for all my cleaning/vacuuming needs!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1Jj1RNANOCTJPjdo8u2vH3zS0_Hurmcz4jl1MC1RG0LGjdMoKPlp5J2dT4DAW-XtveOnM_Ek9nagZdPlX0dLPLpJn8OZUJDbudp8Ern5SBsDlVOU9qt4g9Vyc3-gtgIxRrrIV0Yw=k-no"],"When":"2025-6-8"},{"Name":"Wendy G.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXqRwjozy35CxBCGccRyJtKFPxi-NI6S_aRNr4_prXfe4TG1_M=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"All the folks here helped me solve my problem of a dirty filter in my upright Dirt Devil vacuum cleaner purchased in 2018 for my Bothell home.  Owner/Manager Jonathan and his staff of Elliot and Steven solved my problem and at a fair price for the complete cleaning of my vacuum.\n\nI purchased the product 7 years ago at Fred Meyer Stores and they offered no good replacement filters.  SO glad I knew about Redmond Vacuum. Even close to the Christmas Holiday, they fixed it in record time!  Thank you,  Redmond Vacuum!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
