rBh87eI4PPt6T_J1EXg6Sjw=w224-h298-k-no"},{"title":"By owner","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAFCMfqPkkoTuX-4Tksgzj-axvSldBSuHqWwJ4qysZjj3IELXB-lg7AguQy7M96EQ9smYkJMEa07EwbXrjE7ZCZhQfZzOxL-aD3dZ4imiQITDwflxqdurTM2bkleGVH5xCVF7PG-LA=w397-h298-k-no"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"113633621560295817832","name":"Simple Solutions Plumbing (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113633621560295817832"},"complete_address":{"borough":"","street":"","city":"","postal_code":"","state":"","country":""},"about":[{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Repair services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Virginia G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXWsENDGx9VJvEiyi_83WaPtbd3J5jQb5huAar4lornaPMhBfL5=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Scott and Jon are outstanding plumbers. We had a 1952 house completely replumbed...new everything. Scott walked through the entire plan with us before hand. He is honest and fair and found ways we could save money while getting exactly what we wanted. His knowledge and advise were invaluable. We were able to completely trust that his work was the highest quality at the very best price possible.\nThey notified us when they would arrive each day, and were always on time. Scott called me several times to give me an update on the work and to answer questions. The work space was always clean at the end of day.\nThe greatest endorsement came from the electrician that working at the same time....\"You have the best plumber I've ever worked along side.  His work was outstanding and such a nice person to coordinate the job with.\" (Our electrician has been in business nearly 50 years.)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Margie Wetherald","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVOCbFouY9z7_8J866Thwm6sT631r9-ZroKRsrV8HKK7KEY1LcU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Scott was terrific. He helped me from the start with bathroom faucet replacement. I didn't know which type of faucet I needed or where to look at options. He talked me through the process by phone so I knew where to go and what to do. His installation was straight forward and well executed. I'm so glad I called Simple Solutions.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Claudia Christianson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLfWcZFL2SBs6--eg4w5-8TkRfdVLXTtgqoc0Ae81X8i8vgSQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We love Simple Solutions Plumbing and have hired them on three different occasions. The office is quick to respond to our scheduling needs, the charges are reasonable, and we are always happy with the work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kiran Chitluri","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVmQ5B3n6ACPAnKr6_K7g4TDZ8fTiksuHYbqeziOcl6nPzHk00eTw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Scott is a really experienced and honest plumber.  He is thoughtful and able to be straight with his customers.  I called him for a sewer gas issue in our basement bathroom.  Rather than upsell me for a bunch of work that probably wouldn’t help, he took a methodical approach of eliminating causes and thinking about the issue holistically.  He recommended isolating a couple of potential causes and taking a wait and see approach to see if it was caused by not using the bathroom much. Only after we still experience an issue would he recommend doing some smoke testing.  I was impressed with both his knowledge,  wisdom, and customer focused approach. I wish I had called him sooner and will be going to him in the future for all my plumbing needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shirley Sterkel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW73VDBCeZZ_0jsRFUMuVoU3w0nbon6fklIkGBW5ALoE5Sh_V3e9w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Karla is so expert and helpful in supporting our major water leak.  Thank you so much Simple Solutions Plumbing.  Jon arrived even sooner than the estimated time, found the issue, had the correct valve replacement in hand, and expertly fixed our problem!  Jon knows his stuff!  Easy to talk to and gave us great information.  We could not ask for anyone better -- this company is top notch!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jennifer Reyer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU2rQngCP5JZqvSZPiNnJy4t8-S-3DMSoFk-TSvsuxwLmPvG1QP=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We needed someone to look at very old plumbing and advise on next steps. Simple Solutions came out very quickly and gave advice on how to proceed.  Old plumbing can be easily damage so we needed someone who understood this.  Very please with the outcome","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Wesley Van Voorhis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXOrAsj2seYEl5q24PP9oe_nnOPxWftbZQwnbinwicDI0hPn4Xv=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Scott at Simple Solutions Plumbing was friendly, and knowledgeable. We had tried four other plumbers before him. All wanted to sell us a new on demand water heater system. Scott was an expert in our Bosch gas on demand water heater and fixed it beautifully and expertly. It wasn’t so simple, as the picture shows!  I would definitely recommend him for plumbing help!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1hGumDtX3JknJc8juiXdMLORghFbplRgKPpv2NgiaYlxzS-7-Ley3wMZT4KlYoLSJhiKxFJ1iRjxR4nmeMwL1mi4aV-NLS5c-SPgXTkgmYZq6q2Iqg2FKWVpRB7TEjY-yIF3vSkw=k-no"],"When":"2025-2-20"},{"Name":"Marie Jefferson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWr_bbvFobNtK6nMjyCcQQ5NRmHcwde71PASKZ83jCRAjk-mqQlqg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been working with Scott for nearly 30 years at my mulit-family buildings. He has always worked hard and made solutions that work for me. This project was no surprise, got my tenants water back in less than a day. Thanks Scott! You Rock!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn07GCwUHOkCMJIkJK886KujbGYxXRtvNbnJF8REPpOOz2JkReFeKflN8ZC4-EK-KmpxrtXkeiUm7PFLmF0UX47vot5UTbst1P7Ysib5i3vojBkNAOV63jJPc6QZpS3lfFE6aqvJ=k-no"],"When":"2025-2-14"}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
