effectively able to unclog a toilet when my cheap auger didn’t work. As luck would have it, my kitchen sink clogged up the next day. Sam was able to come out and assess the problem and knew exactly what to do. He gave a quote upfront and got to work. He stayed to test that everything would work as intended. I will always choose Sam with Resolution Plumbing if I ever need a plumber. I wished I would have found him sooner!!\nJennifer Riley","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rita Hagen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLwxAlc8x2qUwwH2hiNOD2EuqOcTMF4n0phtE0l5dfIz53uoQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sam was the best call I ever made for a plumber.  Friendly, professional,  and a wealth of helpful knowledge.  Very reasonable prices. Sam replaced water shutoff valve,  and installed pressure regulator.  He even took the time to fit in two other plumbing issues. He's the one to call!  He should get a 10 star rating. 😉\nRita H.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Teresa Markham","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJHplLkAEUVX0LfdNIseGc5d6KTdo1xVegi_Nfsx8gSuKjEPw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I hired Sam to help diagnose and fix the cause of a mysterious water leak which caused significant damage to a new home I purchased. Sam was fantastic to work with! He came to the home twice so we could find and document via You Tube video that faulty installation of a plumbing fixture by the builder was the cause. Sam was knowledgeable and efficient in diagnosing and fixing the problem, and his expert testimony resulted in the builder finally accepting full responsibility for the issue and reimbursing me for the damage they caused. While this was a bit of an odd plumbing need, I would absolutely hire Sam again for ANY plumbing need. He's friendly, responsive, communicative, and knows his stuff!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mike Tackett","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX5_5SVncG8ZbWVaMeAaXLOXbhKJAuQhq97dYBmcvo0lrYJ6xM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I called Resolution Plumbing late one afternoon about a faulty hose bib, and Sam Scilley — the owner himself — arrived right on schedule the next morning at 10:00 AM. That quick response was impressive, but the level of care and thoroughness he brought to the job went far beyond my expectations.\nSam repaired and replaced the hose bib, explained how to maintain it properly, and patiently answered all my questions with clear, complete explanations. Before wrapping up, he checked the pressure on both front and back hose bibs, inspected the kitchen faucet and identified a broken spring in the spray head (providing the part number and info on how to get a free replacement), cleaned the water heater filter, and gave tips to keep everything running smoothly.\nHe also offered helpful recommendations for better sink stoppers in the bathrooms and suggested a reliable local place to purchase home appliances. In short, there was hardly a plumbing or home water concern he didn’t provide insight on, and I was impressed with his knowledge, professionalism, and thoroughness throughout.\nMy search for a dependable plumber is officially over — I’ll be calling Sam for any plumbing needs in the future. Highly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bill Johnson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJgBLsikPxBDyTXGBEhaIHFkedXE9BtsBRuNES7ynmKwYd5YQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've used Sam's plumbing services for my older home three time over the past few years and the experience has consistency been great. Easy to schedule, reliable, quality workmanship, a great communicator and all at a reasonable price. Would highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eric S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIQff_FWpeUXlcD-vkdxshyLpRPjecWvHF0oifrPGqCUHe1Eg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Resolution Plumbing has helped me with several projects over the past few years as I’ve updated 3 bathrooms and a kitchen; most recently with the installation of a new toilet. Sam is very knowledgeable in all things plumbing and does great work. Highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jeremy Draxler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUmiOwPoOboz7N04IpvwgdF4dRzlFTW2YW9dFY5jZ3WToXaszk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sam was amazing, incredibly happy we called him.\nThe price was fair, and he handled all the weird plumbing issues of a mother in law suite with aplomb. Answered all our non-plumber questions with patience and explained everything clearly.\n\nSam made what can be a stressful situation into a Very simple day.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
