erything was done with care, and it’s clear they take pride in doing the job right. The attention to detail was excellent—they didn’t cut corners, and it shows in the final result.\n\nWe felt confident throughout the entire project, and the end result exceeded our expectations. Highly recommend to anyone looking for high-quality work with great service to match!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nick Chhabra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVTqorV_ET07TJm6MJ0UIBX50hhKZZv_mAmuSjzgnuZYyxLIJ7D=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We hired Hays and Sons, LLC (Ernesto and Harrison) for a home project after a friend’s recommendation, and they were fantastic to work with. They were punctual, polite, professional, and left no mess behind. The quality of their work was great, and their pricing was fair. We are very happy with the results and will definitely call them again for future home projects. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
