 very reasonable prices on repair and remodeling services.\n\nAfter a water damage incident in our basement laundry room, we needed a bunch of drywall repair and new flooring. After a few months of going to the laundromat, we decided to get the laundry room repaired first.\n\nAdolfo gave reasonable timelines and estimates for everything and we were impressed with the amount of work he got done everyday as a 1-man team. He's a genuine person and just wonderful to work with. He did a great job with the drywall and tiling the laundry room.\n\n(Unfortunately I had to remove one star because the last day when he applied texture to the drywall, he didn't cover any of the light switches/plumbing/electrical outlets so the flecks of texture got everywhere)\n\nUpdate: Adolfo reached out to address my concerns and offered to provide additional cleanup. Many contractors would either not respond or give excuses so I updated my rating :)","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2ZSRokGZ3HiZ2SQcRBhr7fJaN6-jkyIe6oV3DYikiYRzh0DENQeF031u5NN2DmCB4e8wpS4HlFRIJbFTGgy20QEAq5ETBdcQJ_PX-3PQBsrPtvNzqt8Uwf5OnA2lXdfPHVQETaRw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2rUzCIcTgyu8RMdgWHlh0-GBR96jVQLUbkvc4HbdPecyAgXR1F6mSBBVzUMPr6YxpZ4n4pzEnI-rTIf82-CXsFL_WTO5E3pvwo1syRis9-Y00DCaBkmNiqHp40NEiFDEnWhRdD=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3cJdml5D6BlutdbgnkyWE0mc9rld_Eqnw5R3BeyL1kcRDw6DMa05z1OXB1a_ldztlmheShSD-7iFWNTuPqAPF-hcralaj5hL5YOJQ26F4LE8-P4FZDCj8XSFlxCCZCb6P1ipohfw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0BjwiYuoeCBZg_TSHVk9mISHCNME53N1EjZv6rIojrvfEQ3gUi0Wo_ZOMl15jF5TuIiM4vn1IRUpTtDCex73xn1ZOMC7BPsgTctwIpgldTAt3Mhk8ewV0lc04zehiGZA_SWZAy=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0Qm7eP1ztHlFFS5Tt1AFGYsm8PDguQ7ssHoWW1od6KQ2h2hLxdddHpv-XNa7oZKtAGbO8WjNOWcWV_OXkF-U6D5yhXjv70UjR9xtGU8A6LyibP_LItNqu2vkkb9Jf8ZcpbmAwGcw=k-no"],"When":"2023-11-22"},{"Name":"Karthik Narasimhan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXL-Us9tguw-oVtIWF125CF6mt9YrRVa2Cf08wEWYctk_zx8L2k=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Adolfo and his team did a great job with the deck and patio repair/re-model. He is knowledgeable, professional, and communicated well before and through out the project. He also referred me to other service providers for a couple of other issues found during the repair work which was very helpful. I would highly recommend Adolfo and his team to anyone looking for remodel/repair work based on his excellent service.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Robert Berg","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJeDgc36jldq9ciCzsiJH1bOU_PXbjVuCathyYfa8v7lEcMHA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had to have my home replumbed after having water damage due to leaky pipes in my laundry room and under my house.  This meant that I had to have my laundry room walls and floor replaced as well as having all of the holes in my drywall in my kitchen, laundry room and upstairs bedroom and had repairs made in my crawl space.\n\nAdolfo and his team were professional and clean and were able to make sure I had use of the kitchen at all times.  He also made sure I was only without a laundry room for 1 week.   He moved the washer and dryer as well as my refrigerator and other items that needed moving and then moved them all back. He is going to be the first person I call for any other repairs I may need in the future.  He is the Best!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brian C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIZvmre4a8I_tDOQtVx7Td-zQOi4lO8CxxQ8J_EdrbPGZYlmg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I typically don’t submit reviews, but how could I not after hiring JD Remodel and Repair. We purchased a home that needed some attention. My research lead us to Adolfo.  He has been over twice for two projects, and even though they were small, he was quick to respond, arrived on time and was both friendly and informative throughout both projects.  His completed work was stellar and his amazing work ethic is rare.  With the small projects out of the way, we have plans to remodel the bathroom. Adolfo is the first person we'll call.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Karyn Schultz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWIzqanG8vaYji7ZQaB7YEE7RlZufjfeCrlL6udDXcxg215xy5D=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We highly recommend working with Adolfo! He quoted us an exact timeline, materials were purchased and prepped prior to day one, site was kept clean and organized, and he even finished the project a day early. He was also so kind and great with our kiddos running around - we will use his services again!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Matt Gombossy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUUwUd737xKCmgM_vBjl8ad6VoDVKiEWbLSaPgsXIIP_DPR7Rxwuw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Adolfo did an excellent job with my basement drywall. He also textured and primed the walls. From start to finish, very professional work and I'm pleased with the result! Highly recommend JD Remodel and Repair!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
