fessional, clean, and has a very fair price point. Being a residential remodeler, my jobs often have challenges that need creative ideas and confident execution to handle. PJ always goes above and beyond. I recommend PJ to anyone who asks for a plumber. I’d give 10 stars if I could. Hire her!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lancer Supasatit","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLJJ9Wgd5PWJ9VQqULUU211aXUnDM1qB_cTQ1lgd_MCsz99BQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The best price and very honest! Highly recommend","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Anders Isaksen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWhxAvYJT76kizc1UoXduDkceOmjcXpEBtOcdDqehtp_L8nynid=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Friendly, good price, quality work","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Darrell Mirsky","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUALacPPzxrJniMyZxWlX-L8Mb60GttOmy3ZEaGf5FWHG3y9Uao4Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had Ryan plumb for a new tub, shower, and bathroom sink. He also installed a new toilet. Ryan always showed up when he said he would, was very good at communicating, very respectful of my home, and is HONEST. His installation was professionally done, and he cleaned up after each visit.\nRyan also installed a recirculation pump which produces instant hot water to the bathrooms that are located on the opposite side of the house where the hot water tank sits. This now saves us several gallons of water each time we turn on a faucet instead of waiting for the hot water to \"arrive\".\nI higher recommend Ryan for any of your plumbing needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sam Engel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWWLBZv9Zvo9PFj5dp9-CwHISJLiBU61vdzSgUHr_jL9WbA0PNW=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"PJ and the team came to the rescue for me. My home ran into a serious plumbing issue, with a sewer line that needed to be replaced. 