had a sewer back up into the home and had another company get the line clear. They then gave me a crazy high price to dig up and replace the sewer. Luckily I called 2 other plumbing companies and got quotes before deciding to move forward. I found Watertite Plumbing and saw great reviews so I called. Sharif came out, we went over the the scope of work, and he gave me a price. It was a very competitive price and we liked the warranty so we chose Watertite Plumbing to do the work. When the day came to start the work, Sharif called and let me know he was on the way, he showed up ontime, and he worked hard digging a big hole. Sharif was pleasant and communicated well throughout the entire project. He even saved a tree that both other companies said they would have to remove. I will use Watertite again and recommend you get a quote from them before you do any work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Laura B.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK0ZmVV-8ZmqUj49b4xCljVlqF0ydI5vUMpK6NomWlXAg05Rw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Huge thanks to Watertite Plumbing! My water heater was leaking and they came out fast to fix it. Super friendly, fair pricing, and the new water heater replacement works great. If you need a local plumber near Seattle, these are the guys to call.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nell Byler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUDR96ICHo-jiDTW9R0kmxTwJTW0GBfZ2YrsVdMNCtHmeiOA3U_9A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sharif is friendly and insightful, fast at communication and very fairly priced. Sharif caught several quirks of our system that other plumbing bidders missed and despite some unexpected hurdles in our water heater replacement, he made sure that the job was finished on time. I will absolutely work with Watertite Plumbing again!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jeff Ruehlmann","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKS7b8zTcAJARpzO0c8sdl3WwQ26gB0dVdJ2JRUYmkzIeaqLQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sharif at Watertite is the best! They took care of our old, leaking water heater right away. Pricing was very competitive and cost exactly what he quoted me. The team was polite, explained everything in advance, and did not try to upsell anything. They treated us with respect which, in a semi-emergency plumbing situation, is not always the case with other bigger plumbers. I wholeheartedly recommend the team at Watertite and will use them for all future work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Phoebe L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIDnb3rYDl7NQV9y8DbwQuyIfTncTchk2vShmyP7T1YksqFCg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a slow kitchen drain, and Sharif was incredibly responsive from the start. He arrived promptly, assessed the problem efficiently, and took the time to explain everything in a way that was easy to understand. If you're looking for a plumber who is reliable, knowledgeable, and committed to excellent service, look no further. I highly recommend Watertite Plumbing!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yongbo Li","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8x2M71n-EQYeRXpx9uLA47gLGCRBmvKsCaeisKx4xERQ2dX_K=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I highly recommend Sharif for any types of plumbing job needed. He did an awesome job with my tub. He is always prompt in response, patient in answering all my questions. His quote price is competitive to begin with. Further, in the process, after he realized the job is easier than initially estimated, he actually reduced the price without being asked. I really appreciate Sharif's honesty, patience and professionalism. I am now confident to treat Sharif as my go-to plumber, and recommend anyone to work with him as well.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Karl Hoffrey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYkXyaGcV43pMQXiDL9nBelv0kIIgOnni9hIPJzS7XEhaXwTCp=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sharif was great, quick response, fair price.  As a person who takes on a lot of my own home repairs I really appretiated that he took  extra time to show me how he was doing the work and tips for a propriety pipe system connections.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amy Hyden","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUzDGkZfCSyay58xMvNtJaSn2hIkEU1v1kstnmVM3rxZQaoH9Y=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sharif was wonderful!  It can be very difficult to find a great plumber, and now I have one with Watertite Plumbing!  Sharif was friendly, professional, prompt, and provided a reasonable quote.  I am so happy with his services and will happily hire him again or give out his name to anyone seeking a great plumber!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
