{"Name":"Tia Gargiulo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUOOKgHcPYx6_7Kie43KTkuGEGdX1yjtGcEes1TQsdRwBIghg4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"When I purchased a home in Mountlake Terrace, it had quite a few badly needed updates, upgrades and repairs related to plumbing.  Michele was there from the beginning and instantly became my house's plumbing subject matter expert.  She is the epitome of trustworthy, professional, capable, helpful and responsive.  Beyond her professional integrity, Michele is simply a wonderful person.  One quick anecdote demonstrative of Michele's dedication and service level: I emailed with an inquiry and within less than an hour she was at my front door despite the fact that it was early morning (during the weekend, no less!).  She checked out the situation in her pajama pants, gave me a run-down of what would need to be done and returned that week with the piece needed to complete the job.  Everyone would be lucky to have a plumber like Pipe Wench Plumbing in their neighborhood.  :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kate Donnelly Klink","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXAECqCIto_-vwNvbQv_O6Vxpf-iE4pCjaSrc6F9Zs2kUhD71Qo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Finally, hot water upstairs without running the tap for 5 min! Pipe Wench installed a new 50 gal water heater for us efficiently and with spotless workmanship. Michele is experienced, responsive, knowledgeable, friendly, and reliable. This is the third job we've had done. Pipe Wench is our go-to plumber.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alex McDermott","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIZcl55m23DLlao6j6_fA1LrH5i6GmQPCRdRUmHf-i3KXVP5Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"An amazing plumber!\nMichelle fixed the clog in the kitchen sink.  Even though it was way more complex and time consuming that what we initially thought, she didn’t overcharge me.  Professional, honest and knows what she’s doing.  Will use again and recommend to anyone- Hope you call her first before the big companies.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Robert Mc Bride","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI6I3qzk9-P1Aehj_2CsXr6HVOSpDvJqlnUXfaWLt0GXn602A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Admittedly I have not hired her to come to my home and make any repairs, however, I had what I feel is a very unique and very surprising experience with this business.  Just over a week ago I accidentally got our Sink Disposal jammed, I had tried what little I knew to try and resolve the jam myself to no avail, so I called to get a quote for replacing the unit, what surprised me was her desire to be helpful over the phone in helping to talk me through unjamming the unit myself as if she wanted to help prevent me from paying to get it fixed, she wanted to save me money by helping me over the phone!  Any other business I have called in the past has always been more than happy to just take my money with no real interest in how it might affect me or my family!  If and when I ever have need of a Plumber in the future I will be calling Pipe Wench Plumbing!  That is a guarantee!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Robin McMurchie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXoIrU94Gpt_8pP7tjFFdWKnw6CUwmAtTR9EcAbP10zYFJm2xs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Michelle came to our rescue when another company bailed on us. The problem was in a wall, not under the house. When I mentioned that we needed water cleanup beyond what we could do, Michelle helped us find a great company. She's incredible!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Desiree Phair","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVDnYKJ32kqjQU7tHOdbS1XFoeXYEosnsR1iGIDnHyNF2RsI1Sx=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The plumber was absolutely amazing and we were always extremely satisfied. Unfortunately, the phone number no longer works, and w