are and expedition in fixing the problem. He is a great guy too.\n\nI would highly recommend him for any job small to big as I am confident he’ll fix it for a fair price, and in a timely fashion.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Matt Olson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXuhWz6dtEOOqYXdTOk7T87cO6avXn1FX-sNrmjxUsrF17tpqQA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"James serviced our water heater. He did a great job for a reasonable price. Will use him for plumbing work in the future.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"ANNE PENNY","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUzs9gFOafXdkpr9XH6Evi7ZSXUc8HXdfje1I0Gd2Cptl7S9xZ5=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is the plumbing service I have ever worked with. They are super smart and efficient. They came quickly, worked on several drains that were badly clogged and got everything draining properly. Polite, cleaned up afterwards, and good prices!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
