ils and helps guide us through our decisions.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Farhad Merchant","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUlyh0FDVOM_mSAIa6MEDKj6QCgcMMPUEf7Kb2ufvWKt7dhKP98=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great experience all around. Hired Charles to help with assembling and installing a Murphy bed system,and then after that went well I also hired him again to help with a backyard camera install. He did a great job with both projects and with the bed he explained where there were flaws in the manufacturing (which enabled me to contact the manufacturer and get replacement/additional parts). It was easy to schedule, had good communication over text, and transparent/fair pricing. Totals for both jobs were in line with the upfront estimates. Very glad to have found a reliable handyman to have on call for household projects. Will gladly refer him to all my friends and family.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kristine Bammert","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKgxJPs2zEsoMrKUDJgZ6SkqlwWWw77ohlEsK7oZJnv4z1iZg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve had the pleasure of seeing Charles twice in the past month.  He’s a good guy and he knows how to fix things! Glad I found Mike’s Handyman Services and have let friends know how pleased I’ve been.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amanda Mary","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUh73P6avLstY6hw_VPjJ13xDQAqHKXapuw722emSNS0zRHlFCojA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I  had a great experience using Mike’s Handyman Services. Charles helped with some small projects like hanging shelves , fixing a broken cabinet drawer and installing carbon monoxide detectors. He was very knowledgeable and thorough, I will definitely be reaching out again for future projects.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kelly Arnold","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ4AvNi445ZIecqSBEmj7ubgj7abNUCKYG1E2px4XooS38q5w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Charles was great! Wonderful thoughtful service that was quick and thorough. Will definitely use again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Theresa Cowger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUNnDU6gFHLvaNM8-vyNrvxOiMj67mNxNbZmptG_MyimrTQmsSe=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I just had Charles from Mike’s Handyman come and fix a broken closet clothes rod.  Charles did an excellent job putting the broken pieces together.  He went the extra mile to go to Home Depot to buy a\nStrong wooden  dowel.  He literally made the closet better than it was before.  Charles was a consummate professional.  I highly recommend Charles and Mike’s Handyman if you need a smalll project done.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Erin Hayashi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJFZZ4WbOz2xb6JDIsNBTHJ9UXzZUVxzlAsjGPfiNP-4ShCvw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We were looking for someone to install a frameless sliding shower door in our newly renovated bathroom. We had done most of the work ourselves but preferred having a professional do the door. Charles had exactly the expertise we needed! He ended up spending nearly 8 hours on the job, which turned out to be difficult due to the extra hard tile we installed. He was kind and professional the entire time, and the shower door turned out amazing. Closes beautifully and looks great. Plus the price was fair! So glad we asked for help from Charles!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jerry Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUCwJZP5coe59XTLc5kXie6Ih_nngQsjfMtJ-N4U-DaLpkwJ2aHRQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We hired Mike's Handyman Services to replace two toilets. Charlie arrived right on time and communicated the price very clearly. The installation was performed quickly and smoothly, and he also repaired a bit of mis-installed pieces from before. He also squeezed in a quick repair of our shed door.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
