ouse. The quality, design, combined with hard work made an outstanding result in the end. I absolutely love my bathrooms now!\nSami and his team came to me as a referral to me from a friend.\nThe entire team is very friendly and professional. They finished the job and took all my specifications into consideration.\nI couldn't be happier with their work and I am going to recommend them to all my friends and family! Thank you Sami Construction","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3Fgrackb45vZY-o1Q7H83SPqBKfXP3VeZnCAJuZNMY1JIpiGTH8MV44fqLBXPlZHH6kLmRmyXDHqRC9VD8g9oLWwuh00cSeAO7xFwvqh8n5LQav5r2zUt0rn3aNpe5c9BkPP5F=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2JDXTffcLImx2kzerWTqt_gA3Mh-xs_Fe2-BgKWRGcL2wPzS8ruCSTi3RzchU5Dk1LGkonv6HNExwdYMX2HMri9QepzUAIzJUHQq0eLeh86PccEk9DvIeoXPPv4rmTksGLnW8piQ=k-no"],"When":"2021-10-12"},{"Name":"Abhishek Ghosh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWV9zDYo69m-jVc0b_eJcqK6I7DmoyYCkvAwaQCzuZ6K98kvhDz=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sami did a bathroom remodel job at our home. He did an awesome job from the planning phase to the final execution. He is detail oriented, cost conscious, sticks to planned budget/timelines and overall has a great attitude really wanting to do a high quality job for complete customer satisfaction. He even went over and beyond and fixed a leakage issue at the bathroom unrelated to his project. Overall, we are very happy with his work at our home and strongly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aruna Ambalavanan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL2f6eLOOaPsCkwrUUuLs20kBv2OWX-J_CwbM2fzVAfGP8mELa3=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Josh and team were very professional and completed our projects on time. They were open to suggestions and asked for our feedback. we started remodeling our master bath, in due course we changed the vanity in the guest bath, installed new lights in our bedroom. All these