o matter how many complications your old house throws at him. He does his research on the best way to accomplish the job so you know he's giving you the best option. Plus, he's just a straight-forward, honest, friendly guy who you can trust in your home. I strongly recommend him to friends, family, or anyone I know looking for plumbing work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dave Desmon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK5gvcIswiMwO7x4f8jJapl-Yz6uVrhtHOVnr8S-dAO6cvuZg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Brian and his Son worked us in quickly on an emergency repair.  We've had him out several times on various issues over the past few years, and he's always quick, fair, does great work (which he guarantees)  and explains everything up front.\nHighly Recommended!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eamun Rahimi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVqbn0I0QS_Nk36sUKwqmTiBV5_iUtz3nwIcoi6dnN9bvS2Cas1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I'm a big fan of getting a second opinion when necessary. I had one HVAC company give me insight as to my furnace's condition and provided a recommendation but it didn't quite sit well with me - they identified the initial problem but told me it's better to overhaul the system. Brian came the following day, identified the same root cause (without upsell), and actually got the job done versus telling me that I should rework my entire system.\nI haven't used him for plumbing (yet), but he'll be in my address book for any plumbing needs going forward as well.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tamara Wedell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJN-fEaiIYXRThRTwBwDu3JzYKPzfEJH14g6I5WrmBiFqSA7nA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Highly recommend! Very professional and wonderful job!  Will be using Brian's plumbing for my future needs.  Thank you for helping us so quick Brian!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brandon Knowles","