nd Quality House LLC for any home project; wish we would have found them sooner!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Erica Sponsler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIfPW7w8WVHPIFdYR-S2R5KkYdGU5zOXzWlZzmg55vCG3LDZQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We've had Andrew do a variety of jobs around our house over the past several years including cleaning our gutters, painting our porch, and a variety of repairs. He's done a fantastic job every time, he's easy to get in touch with, and his prices are reasonable. I've recommended him to several friends and neighbors over the years, and have only heard good things from them as well. Highly, highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gitika Gupta","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL38OfEFqprWieFtKSSzB51CmFlGBxpfe_BdHpQnk-FtAby-Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Andrew from Quality House has been a pleasure to work with. We did an expansion to bring the patio space into the house and then remodeled the kitchen. Andrew's pricing was very competitive, he worked through all the details, has a good team of people who were punctual and professional, and delivered and completed the project to our satisfaction in good time. I would highly recommend Andrew and his team.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
