rcontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUj0P82_1yAnKfBED5g1Vo6WG3cEc0FYJnqTsRb2C3Uy89zAl8-=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Rey's team at Effective Plumbing came as a recommendation to me to solve a mystery leak. They were able to provide me options on how to proceed when the issues were discovered and explained clearly how these issues could've' occurred. The fees are very reasonable and I plan on calling Effective Plumbing for my future plumbing needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Christy Johnston","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKIbaLsVvzreXMQKZlSWqTsynMjnU02cjS21L3uUpAu0zA4JA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Rey and and his team are reliable, friendly, knowledgeable and kind. They are familiar with all sorts of plumbing issues. I am a property manager with many odd characteristics of a mix of old and new plumbing. I have seen them in action on big and small messes. They go above and beyond to make it work for the customer.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"MFHill Hill","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLWtQPloDw5uktkzbU7rBtdwq7HYHiJY_hK1tf9MhCE3j0UIw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Rey and his crew are the best!  They are experienced in old school plumbing techniques as well as the latest practices.  Always professional, courteous and reliable.  They cleaned up the worksite every day.  In 2023 EP did all the plumbing upgrades for my condo’s kitchen, guest and master bathrooms. They were very patient and understanding when there was a scheduling conflict with another contractor. I am contacting them today to do a small repair on one of my toilets.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Karina Reyes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUqv-B9g_P5UBNRFWycBV5vwA0v570ItuhGYMW3JcFXWTUW7GwZ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"5 Stars – Always Reliable and Friendly!\nI've used Effective Plumbing multiple times over the years, and they have never let me down. Every job they’ve done has been excellent — whether it was a small repair or a larger project, they handled it professionally and efficiently. Their team is awesome — super friendly, respectful, and always happy to answer any questions I have. One thing that really stands out is their pricing — always fair, honest, and some of the best rates around. It’s rare to find a company this consistent, trustworthy, and easy to work with. I highly recommend Effective Plumbing to anyone looking for reliable plumbing services!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Patty Romero","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK2-wAB2E7mYLWB2Q3LI4xe68p7ZVZ37KAF5XKnCw2Mj7psEA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The job done by effective plumbing at my location in Queen Anne was perfect. It really was effective, friendly staff, fast accurate service. I’m very satisfied with their work. I definitely recommend effective plumbing.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"I R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAqYNLEXbB7etpQj2QWGVLhW4MU5BQnby1KPmF1nkdjw3OqnnU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing work, Honest trust worthy and very reliable, thank you !!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Oscar Romero","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXwarC_SsDvyJwt9kN9yZO6WFQRqj2_f7NoXxKH3zModHC0sFyD=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very professional and friendly technicians.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
